UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=4265 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='I don\'t care to hear it, $n. Nope, no way are you going to be let into the Searing Gorge. Impossible. Not going to happen. How many times do I have to tell you - I can\'t let you in! Do you not speak common? Are you an orc in disguise? N-O. NO!$B$BIf I let you in, then I have to let everybody in. Pretty soon your close friends will want in, then their distant relatives, then their friends, and so on and so forth. The last time that happened... well, we won\'t talk about the last time it happened. ';
