UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5179 SET `male_text`='Greetings, $c. For some, the hunter is a way of life, a chosen profession. For others, it is something of a pastime, a badge of courage, or a rite of passage depending on your tribe.$B$BFor me, race and profession mean nothing--it is the testing of your spirit and mind that I respect. For one to stand against the forces of nature and test all of their skills is the true mark of honor.$B$BIf you wish to test yourself and earn my respect, then speak to me more.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5181 SET `male_text`='You\'ve started down an honorable path, $n. My ancestors respect your willingness, but you will not have my approval until you have followed through with my tasks.$B$BYou know what you must do if you wish to prove yourself a hunter in spirit.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5182 SET `male_text`='I give you warm greetin\'s, $c, as does the Shattered Hand.$B$BDo not look so surprised, $n. There be shadows even on the highest perches of Orgrimmar--somethin\' must hide there. The Shattered Hand take that role willingly. Thrall, even in his good heart, acknowledge that the Hand be necessary to ensure orc and troll safety.$B$BBut you not here to talk \'bout my business, you here for somethin\' else.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5183 SET `male_text`='Un\'Goro Crater be far to the south of Kalimdor. Beyond the Thousand Needles in Tanaris. Look for the large floating stones... they mark the entrance to the Crater. But be careful... it is no easy path. The raptors are not far from the entrance.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5184 SET `male_text`='Where is Un\'Goro Crater?', `female_text`='Where is Un\'Goro Crater?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5185 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Thanks to you, we can now unlock the secrets of the crystals and the mysterious pylons, $n. If you need more information at any time, please come back and visit me again!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5186 SET `male_text`='Tell me more about the Eastern Crystal Pylon.', `female_text`='Tell me more about the Eastern Crystal Pylon.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5187 SET `male_text`='Who is this Lar\'korwi you spoke of?', `female_text`='Who is this Lar\'korwi you spoke of?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5188 SET `male_text`='Tell me more about the Northern Crystal Pylon.', `female_text`='Tell me more about the Northern Crystal Pylon.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5189 SET `male_text`='The ravasaur here in Un\'Goro seem to be related to the raptors of the barrens--highly intelligent, volatile, and with a sense or code of conduct. The greatest of these that I have encountered is  Lar\'korwi. He is one of the most dangerous beasts I\'ve ever seen. In taurahe, Lar\'korwi means \"sharp claw, `female_text`='" but that does not do him justice.$B$BDo not underestimate Lar\'korwi if you ever plan on hunting him, but I will help you in any way I can if you do.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5190 SET `male_text`='Tell me more about the Western Crystal Pylon.', `female_text`='Tell me more about the Western Crystal Pylon.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5191 SET `male_text`='I lost my Crystal Pylon User\'s Manual and need another one.', `female_text`='I lost my Crystal Pylon User\'s Manual and need another one.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5192 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='The Eastern Pylon accepts blue, yellow, and green crystals.$B$BIt focuses on the energy that can be created using blue crystals as the main source of power. There are two possible effects: one provides bonus to spirit, and one that creates a damaging shield.$B$BCrystal Force requires blue and green crystals. This will provide you with an increase in spirit.$B$BCrystal Spire requires blue and yellow crystals. This will create a shield that does damage to attackers.\n\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5193 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='The Northern Pylon accepts yellow, red, and green crystals.$B$BThe focus is the energy that can be created using yellow crystals as the main source of power. There are two possible effects: one that will produce damage, and one that will negate damage. $B$BCrystal Charge requires red and yellow crystals. This will produce a large explosion, stunning your enemies.$B$BCrystal Restore requires yellow and green crystals. This will provide you with a healing aura.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5194 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='The Western Pylon accepts red, green, and blue crystals.$B$BThe Pylon focuses on the energy that can be created using red crystals as the main source of power. There are two possible effects: one that increases your protection from damage, and one that weakens an enemy\'s defenses.$B$BCrystal Ward requires red and green crystals. This will provide you with an increase to armor.$B$BCrystal Yield requires blue and red crystals. This can lower the armor of a specific target.';
