UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5432 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hello there, my name is Petra.  To my right is my kodo, Dadanga.  We\'re with Marshal Expeditions - been so for a few years now, ever since Dadanga was a babe.$B$BIf you have any lit torches or any open sources of flame, I\'d like to ask you to keep them stashed if you could.  Dadanga dislikes smoke.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5433 SET `male_text`='For the love of all that is holy and dear, please tell me that you\'ve come to deliver us from this forsaken land.  Though I\'m with Marshal Expeditions, I would give you the gold teeth from my mouth to climb inside your backpack and leave this place.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5434 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Oh, hello there!  I\'m Hol\'anyee, the chief scientist and biologist of Marshal Expeditions.  My brother and I, along with our companions, travel Azeroth exploring the wild and untamed majesty.  It is exciting... but, um... I think we got ourselves into a little too much excitement this time!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5435 SET `male_text`='Hello stranger, and welcome to the untamed majesty of Un\'Goro Crater!$B$BMy name is Williden Marshal.  My sister, our companions, and I make up Marshal Expeditions - scientists and explorers of Azeroth\'s wild and great unknown.$B$BWe\'ve hit a bit of a rough patch here, and we\'re looking for some help if you have the time!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5436 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='This is where things get interesting.  My plan is to follow the mountail wall, keeping it to our left.  That way, we won\'t get lost in the jungle and we\'ll cut down on the hostiles.  You ready?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5437 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Here\'s the eastern mountain wall!  I\'m cutting towards the south now; try and keep up.  We\'re not out of the thick of it yet!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5439 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Here\'s the path out of Un\'Goro!  We made it!  All we have to worry about is the Tanaris desert now.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5440 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Here it is -- the Tanaris desert.  Funny how an inhospitable place like this looks better than a lush jungle once you\'ve been trapped in it forever.';
