UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5448 SET `male_text`='Look at these samples! What does it mean? What does it mean? I\'m going to need time, time to look at all this information. And I\'ll need more information. Information I can\'t get... damn! Think, Laris, think!$B$BWhat are you going to do? What?!$B$BThere has to be a solution!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5449 SET `male_text`='There must be someplace on Azeroth that we can find oozes uncorrupted by the Scourge or anything else. But where?!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5450 SET `male_text`='Is there a difference between ooze and slime?', `female_text`='Is there a difference between ooze and slime?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5451 SET `male_text`='No, not that I can tell. It seems to be mostly based on region. Some races have labled them slimes, some oozes. It seems to be preference mostly.$B$BEvery time I\'ve encountered ooze, sludge, or slime they have basically been the same creatures. The differences seem to be based on their environment, which is why we need a pure sample.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5452 SET `male_text`='What do you mean by \"pure?\"', `female_text`='What do you mean by \"pure?\"';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5453 SET `male_text`='A pure sample would be one that\'s uncorrupted by unintentional influences. We need to find the creatures in the most basic, normal environment we can.$B$BThat means somewhere devoid of civilization or the effects of the dominant races of Azeroth. Someplace... untouched.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5454 SET `male_text`='Are there any areas you can think of that would be so untouched?', `female_text`='Are there any areas you can think of that would be so untouched?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5455 SET `male_text`='It\'ll definitely not be anywhere in the Eastern Kingdoms, that\'s for sure.$B$BIt\'ll have to be somwhere on Kalimdor, but still far enough away from the Horde and other races. Someplace unaffected by the Sundering--that means no where near the Night elves\' civilization either.$B$BI would guess it\'d be someplace protected also... like a valley, or a crater. I don\'t know. I\'m just guessing now. I\'m sorry I couldn\'t help you more.', `female_text`='';
