UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5505 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='I welcome you to Theramore, $n.$B$BI apologize for being abrupt and not having a lot of time to exchange pleasantries, but my city must come first. Too many things threaten our way of life and the sanctity of the Alliance. I must stay ever vigilant against forces outside of our control if I\'m to ensure my people remain safe and happy.$B$BPerhaps we\'ll have more time to speak later.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5506 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hendel is in our custody now, $n, thanks to you.$B$BAlthough the questioning goes slowly, I assure you, he will tell us everything he knows.$B$BFor now, please be patient. I will contact you immediately if we have need of your assistance.$B$BUntil then, please, enjoy Theramore and I invite you to stay for as long as you like within our city\'s walls as a friend of the Alliance.';
