UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5774 SET `male_text`='Ow!  OK, I\'ll get back to work, $n!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5775 SET `male_text`='When I get all shaken up, hear me shout...', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5776 SET `male_text`='Vaelastrasz, when this world belongs to the black flight, your flight shall know its end.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5777 SET `male_text`='But for now, your death will have to suffice...', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5778 SET `male_text`='You merely destroy an image, fool. I shall hunt you until the end of days.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5779 SET `male_text`='Aye, it appears as if ye have learned quite a bit, I\'m impressed. But do ye know how many I have that seek to be my apprentice? Tell ye what, do a small task fer me and I\'ll take ye on.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5780 SET `male_text`='Ye have some skill about ye with hammer and anvil, but not enough. Go speak to Dane Lindgren, he\'ll get ye ready to learn what I have to teach ye.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5781 SET `male_text`='I said ye had the blood of a blacksmith in ye, and I was right. Go to Ironforge, to The Great Forge, and find yerself a Dwarven smith by the name of Bengus Deepforge. My teacher, and one of the greatest smiths I\'ve ever known.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5783 SET `male_text`='The life of a smith is not an easy one, but it puts steel in yer bones and fire in yer heart. My da\' was a smith, my grandfather before him in the forges beneath Grim Batol. And now my son follows in our footsteps, that boy makes me proud.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5784 SET `male_text`='Sorry $g lad : lass;, ye aren\'t quite up to the challenge of learning from me. Go see my son Groum, it would make his day to get a new apprentice.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5785 SET `male_text`='Yer skill is not without merit, but I need to put one last test to ye before I take ye on.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5786 SET `male_text`='Aye, I would love ta teach ye a thing or two about smithing. Grab an apron and a hammer and let\'s see what we can accomplish shall we?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5787 SET `male_text`='A fast learner is what ye are, and a good smith to boot. I would sign off on yer work any day of the week. But I sense ye still have some learnin in ye. Go talk to Bengus Deepforge, he\'s a hard taskmaster but he\'s also one of the best.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5788 SET `male_text`='%s lets out a shrill cry.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5789 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Don\'t come out of the shadows like that. Next time give a girl some warning. ';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5790 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Ever since the shadows claimed Duskwood I haven\'t been able to sleep. I am kept awake by the ghostly sounds of screaming on the breeze. It sounds almost like lambs screaming, and they won\'t stop.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5791 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hmm, your work is allright but it\'s nowhere near the quality I look for in a student. Go talk with Smith Argus in Goldshire, I\'m sure he can teach you some basics. Then when you\'re done, come on back to me and I\'ll give you a little test to make sure you are ready.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5792 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Yeah, I\'ve heard through the grapevine that I might be seeing you sooner or later. But I don\'t just take on anyone, I need to make sure you have what it takes first. You willing to take my little test and find out?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5793 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='You do fine work, but it\'s a bit rough around the edges. Don\'t worry about it, it will come with practice. Speaking of which, how about we see what you\'ve been working on?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5794 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Now I\'m the one who feels rough around the edges, I honestly don\'t think there\'s anything left I can teach you. But you know who can? Bengus Deepforge in Ironforge, now there\'s a dwarf that knows his steel. Go look him up in The Great Forge of Ironforge, see if he\'s up to having a new trainee under him.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5795 SET `male_text`='If I prove myself to Saru he will have no choice but to let me fight for one of his daughters. Then we will see who is sneering.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5796 SET `male_text`='Stay away from Sumi and Tumi. They are....spoken for.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5797 SET `male_text`='Come to me again with such pathetic work and I will send you home in a small iron box that I tempered in goat urine. Now go see that idiot Ug\'thok, he is better suited to your needs.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5798 SET `male_text`='So you think you are good enough to learn from me? The great Snarl? You are no more than a lowly worm beneath my boot. However, taking on an underling might make me seem more appealing to Sumi and Tumi. Let\'s see what meager skills you possess.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5799 SET `male_text`='Hmm? Oh yes, I can teach you something if you desire. But stay away from Sumi and Tumi, they are not for the likes of you. Saru only let\'s those of great skill approach his daughters.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5800 SET `male_text`='There is nothing more that I can teach - now get out! And don\'t even think of approaching Saru, for one as unworthy as you he will use your blood to temper his steel.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5801 SET `male_text`='The spirits have brought you to me, and so I feel blessed by them. ', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5803 SET `male_text`='You need to heed the guidance of the spirits a little better young one. Your path lies with another, Thrag Stonehoof in Thunder Bluff. Perhaps you can learn something from one another.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5805 SET `male_text`='Tell me, do your feel prepared to face the challenge I have laid out for you? The spirits tell me that you will pass, but do you have faith in them or in yourself?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5806 SET `male_text`='Join me, together we will weave the spirits of the forge and find the true shape that the metal seeks.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5807 SET `male_text`='Our paths through life intersect only briefly and now is the time for ours to part ways. I consider myself blessed to have spent this time teaching you and now send you along to join paths with your next mentor. Seek out Saru Steelfury of Orgrimmar, he will teach what you need to learn.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5808 SET `male_text`='You have great potential, but you must achieve understanding first, you must accept the spirits and listen to their calling. Only then will you be prepared for the path you must follow. Go speak with Thrag, I think perhaps you can learn a lot from one another.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5809 SET `male_text`='You are now ready to follow the path that joins your life with my own, if only for a short time. However we must make sure that you understand the things of which the spirits speak.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5810 SET `male_text`='You have learned much, but I sense that there is more left for the spirits to teach you. I can place your foot on the path but cannot guide your steps. Go and find Saru Steelfury in Orgrimmar, the next stretch of your journey begins there.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5811 SET `male_text`='You waste my time, go talk with my student Basil.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5812 SET `male_text`='Perhaps you have what it takes, perhaps not. If you do then I will take you on and teach you what you wish to know. If you do not... well, I\'ll just leave it at that.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5813 SET `male_text`='Very fine equipment you make, very fine indeed. Go to the Orc\'s home of Orgrimmar and seek out a smith named Saru Steelfury. One thing you must give the Orcs, they make beautiful instruments of death.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5814 SET `male_text`='I\'m sorry $g lad : lass; but ye just don\'t have the foundation to learn what I have to teach. But don\'t fret, go speak with my student Rotgath, he\'ll help ye out.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5815 SET `male_text`='Looks like ye may have the makings of a great smith. But before I teach ye anything I need to know that ye\'ve got what it takes. ', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5816 SET `male_text`='I can\'t say enough about yer work, truly amazing things that ye can do with a hammer and an anvil. Now, don\'t be tellin anyone that I suggested ye go find a goblin to teach ye but that\'s exactly what I\'m gonna do. Brikk Keencraft is his name, and last I heard he was operating a shop down in Booty Bay.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5817 SET `male_text`='This isn\'t a game you toy with youngling! Go, speak with Snarl outside. He may be a serpent in my lair but he does know his way around an anvil.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5818 SET `male_text`='Still a bit weak, unbalanced, unsure. Not your work youngling, I am speaking of you! Now, are you ready to be shaped into a real smith or not?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5819 SET `male_text`='I see you know more of the secret of steel than I do. That is good, for it is meant to be taken. Now you must travel to the jungle south of the human lands, to the goblin city of Booty Bay. There you will find a Goblin named Brikk Keencraft. I do not like Goblins but his knowledge of the secret of steel is unmatched by any I know of.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5820 SET `male_text`='Yeah? Of course I\'m a smith. What, you think Dwarves are the only ones worth their weight in anvils? Fine, be that way. Go get a dwarf to help you!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5821 SET `male_text`='Are you kidding me? You must be kidding me! Either that or you think I\'m a clown here to amuse you. Is that what you think? That I\'m a clown? Huh, is it! You think I\'m a clown don\'t you!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5822 SET `male_text`='You act like this is the best junk I\'ve ever seen. Sure it\'s ok, but I see stuff this \'OK\' every day. Tell you what, you find a way to wow me, and I\'ll teach you things that make dwarves smile in their sleep.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5823 SET `male_text`='Imagination is the limit my friend, if you can figure out how to smith it then you can make it, box it, and ship it to retailers all over the world. Of course, then you have to deal with marketing. Tell you what, let\'s just stick with the smithing part for now, ok?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5824 SET `male_text`='Your victory shall be short lived. The days of both the Alliance and Horde are coming to an end! The next time we meet shall be the last.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5825 SET `male_text`='What did Gryphe tell boss?? Gryphe wasn\'t lying! There she is, trying to steal battle plans!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5826 SET `male_text`='Gryfe do his job! Gryfe go now!!!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5827 SET `male_text`='Oh, it\'s on now! Bet you thought I\'d be alone too, huh?!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5828 SET `male_text`='Whoa! This is way more than what I bargained for, you\'re on your own, Slim!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5829 SET `male_text`='Though I hate to admit it, the bear did get the better of me. My oh my, that\'s one big ol\' bear!$b$bNonetheless, if you can take that bear down, it\'d be a feat to be proud of! It gave more than a few of our best hunters some trouble.$b$b<He claps you on the back.>$b$bBest the bear and we\'ll accept you as a regular member of the Farstrider Lodge.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5830 SET `male_text`='Here at the Farstrider lodge, we prize hunting skills above all else. Wish to gain my approval? You\'ll have to earn it.$B$BYou look up to the challenge, $Glad:lass;!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=5831 SET `male_text`='You\'ve become quite the hunter, $n! Not only have you proven your skills, you also bested Daryl, which gets you extra points in my book!$B$BYou\'re welcome here any time.', `female_text`='';
