UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6315 SET `male_text`='That bum Leland... all he does is sit out on the dock outside the Trade District and fish all day.  I sure hope he\'s good at it for all the time he spends fishing.  If you want to learn, why don\'t you go talk to him?', `female_text`='That bum Leland... all he does is sit out on the dock outside the Trade District and fish all day.  I sure hope he\'s good at it for all the time he spends fishing.  If you want to learn, why don\'t you go talk to him?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6316 SET `male_text`='There\'s nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that\'s what the night elves tell me.  I\'m not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I\'m sure Tannysa could help you out.  She\'s over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs.', `female_text`='There\'s nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that\'s what the night elves tell me.  I\'m not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I\'m sure Tannysa could help you out.  She\'s over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs.';
