UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6319 SET `male_text`='A Hunter is it?  Well, then you will want to speak with Thorfin Stoneshield over in the Dwarven District.  \n\nOh, and you be sure to tell him that if I step in his pet\'s business one more time, he\'s going to be training other hunters from behind bars in the Stockade!', `female_text`='A Hunter is it?  Well, then you will want to speak with Thorfin Stoneshield over in the Dwarven District.  \n\nOh, and you be sure to tell him that if I step in his pet\'s business one more time, he\'s going to be training other hunters from behind bars in the Stockade!';
