UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6323 SET `male_text`='Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he\'s here, he\'s probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District.', `female_text`='Leave it to the dwarves to send a mining specialist from Ironforge to tell us how to mine.  How hard is it to take a pick and chip away at some rock?  Well, since he\'s here, he\'s probably the one you should see anyhow.  His name is Gelman and he resides over in the Dwarven District.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6324 SET `male_text`='You know, I could run an orc through or slice up a troll.  I could even carve my initials in an ogre\'s flank, but I just can\'t stand to skin an animal.  Go figure, eh.  \n\nWell, if you have the stomach for it, then go see Maris Granger at the Protective Hide in Old Town.', `female_text`='You know, I could run an orc through or slice up a troll.  I could even carve my initials in an ogre\'s flank, but I just can\'t stand to skin an animal.  Go figure, eh.  \n\nWell, if you have the stomach for it, then go see Maris Granger at the Protective Hide in Old Town.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6325 SET `male_text`='A tailor is it?  Well, if you hang out here long enough you\'ll eventually hear word of mouth about Georgio Bolero.  He\'s been setting the trends for some months now.  If you wish to learn from him, you can find him over in the Mage Quarter in the outer rim.', `female_text`='A tailor is it?  Well, if you hang out here long enough you\'ll eventually hear word of mouth about Georgio Bolero.  He\'s been setting the trends for some months now.  If you wish to learn from him, you can find him over in the Mage Quarter in the outer rim.';
