UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6333 SET `male_text`='Aye, everyone wants to ride the tram, it\'s a real hoot and a half.  Well, if ye want to find the tram, it\'s located over in Tinker Town just east of the gates of Ironforge.', `female_text`='Aye, everyone wants to ride the tram, it\'s a real hoot and a half.  Well, if ye want to find the tram, it\'s located over in Tinker Town just east of the gates of Ironforge.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6334 SET `male_text`='Oh, the tram, the tram...  everyone wants to ride the tram.  What happened to the good ol\' days of flying on the back of a gryphon, gripping the saddle for dear life as you flew up high in the sky above?  \n\nBah!  You go take the tram then... it\'s over in Tinker Town with the rest of the gnomish contraptions.', `female_text`='Oh, the tram, the tram...  everyone wants to ride the tram.  What happened to the good ol\' days of flying on the back of a gryphon, gripping the saddle for dear life as you flew up high in the sky above?  \n\nBah!  You go take the tram then... it\'s over in Tinker Town with the rest of the gnomish contraptions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6335 SET `male_text`='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  \n\nIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.  ', `female_text`='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  \n\nIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.  ';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6336 SET `male_text`='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.', `female_text`='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6337 SET `male_text`='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  \n\nExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?', `female_text`='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  \n\nExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6338 SET `male_text`='First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me.  If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from.  Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician.', `female_text`='First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me.  If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from.  Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6339 SET `male_text`='I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword.  Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which.  Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was.', `female_text`='I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword.  Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which.  Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6340 SET `male_text`='Well now, ye\'ll need papers to form a guild, and Jondor Steelbrow can help you get started with the process.  He can be found over at the Ironforge Visitor\'s Center when yer ready to get started.', `female_text`='Well now, ye\'ll need papers to form a guild, and Jondor Steelbrow can help you get started with the process.  He can be found over at the Ironforge Visitor\'s Center when yer ready to get started.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6341 SET `male_text`='Do ye have the potential to be a skilled hunter?  Well $gladdie : lassie;, only time will tell.  Just don\'t ye go shooting at apples atop peoples\' heads till ye\'ve spoken with Regnus o\'er in the Hall of Arms.', `female_text`='Do ye have the potential to be a skilled hunter?  Well $gladdie : lassie;, only time will tell.  Just don\'t ye go shooting at apples atop peoples\' heads till ye\'ve spoken with Regnus o\'er in the Hall of Arms.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6342 SET `male_text`='Sure ye don\'t want to be a Blacksmith?  Well, if yer heart is set on Leatherworking, then you best talk to Fimble Finespindle over at his shop on the northwest side of The Great Forge.', `female_text`='Sure ye don\'t want to be a Blacksmith?  Well, if yer heart is set on Leatherworking, then you best talk to Fimble Finespindle over at his shop on the northwest side of The Great Forge.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6343 SET `male_text`='Bah!  Mailboxes...  all I get is junk mail lately!  \n\nIncrease the size of this... decrease the size of that... act now for your free Sword of Dragonslaying.  I have to change my mailbox number every other month!  \n\nWell, ye can\'t say I didn\'t warn ye.  If you\'re looking for the mailbox it\'s just outside the Stonefire Tavern.', `female_text`='Bah!  Mailboxes...  all I get is junk mail lately!  \n\nIncrease the size of this... decrease the size of that... act now for your free Sword of Dragonslaying.  I have to change my mailbox number every other month!  \n\nWell, ye can\'t say I didn\'t warn ye.  If you\'re looking for the mailbox it\'s just outside the Stonefire Tavern.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6344 SET `male_text`='Well well!  You\'ve come to the right place to learn Mining, $gboyo : girlie;!  Geofram Bouldertoe himself resides at the Deepmountain Mining Guild.  Ye couldn\'t ask for a better instructor than him.', `female_text`='Well well!  You\'ve come to the right place to learn Mining, $gboyo : girlie;!  Geofram Bouldertoe himself resides at the Deepmountain Mining Guild.  Ye couldn\'t ask for a better instructor than him.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6345 SET `male_text`='The book tells of dragons uniting against another, more powerful dragon, named Deathwing. From what you can make out, the chromatic dragonflight had almost been unleashed upon the world. The Aspects were prepared.\n', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6346 SET `male_text`='Ah, nothing better than a priest to cure what ails ye.  Of course a nice tall pint cures a lot of what ails ye too, but I don\'t think Braenna Flintcrag teaches brewing.  I guess ye\'ll have to settle for some priest training over in the Hall of Mysteries instead.', `female_text`='Ah, nothing better than a priest to cure what ails ye.  Of course a nice tall pint cures a lot of what ails ye too, but I don\'t think Braenna Flintcrag teaches brewing.  I guess ye\'ll have to settle for some priest training over in the Hall of Mysteries instead.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6347 SET `male_text`='Ye might not know it, but in addition to being a skilled tailor, Jormund is also a slayer of giants!  Why he must have overheard a few of us sharing stories when he shouted that he\'d killed seven with one blow!  \n\nYe should pay him a visit at his store on the north side of The Great Forge an\' see if he\'ll tell ye the tale!', `female_text`='Ye might not know it, but in addition to being a skilled tailor, Jormund is also a slayer of giants!  Why he must have overheard a few of us sharing stories when he shouted that he\'d killed seven with one blow!  \n\nYe should pay him a visit at his store on the north side of The Great Forge an\' see if he\'ll tell ye the tale!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6348 SET `male_text`='Skinning?  The only thing ye look like ye could skin is yer own knee!  Ha!  Now why don\'t you go see Balthus Stoneflayer so he can teach you how to properly skin some animals.  You\'ll find him in Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.', `female_text`='Skinning?  The only thing ye look like ye could skin is yer own knee!  Ha!  Now why don\'t you go see Balthus Stoneflayer so he can teach you how to properly skin some animals.  You\'ll find him in Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6349 SET `male_text`='A warlock, eh...  Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $gboyo : girlie;.  I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them.  Ye get me?  \n\nNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern.  That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart.', `female_text`='A warlock, eh...  Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $gboyo : girlie;.  I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them.  Ye get me?  \n\nNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern.  That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6350 SET `male_text`='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  \n\nI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.', `female_text`='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  \n\nI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.';
