UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6353 SET `male_text`='An alchemist?  No trouble at all $c.  Ainethil, in all her labor and toil, has become the most accomplished alchemist in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.  I would head over there on the double if I were you. On the double!  Now off with you!', `female_text`='An alchemist?  No trouble at all $c.  Ainethil, in all her labor and toil, has become the most accomplished alchemist in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.  I would head over there on the double if I were you. On the double!  Now off with you!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6354 SET `male_text`='Another material $gboy : girl; are we?  Well, if you are obsessed with your precious items then you will probably want to store them at the Darnassus Bank in the center of our city.', `female_text`='Another material $gboy : girl; are we?  Well, if you are obsessed with your precious items then you will probably want to store them at the Darnassus Bank in the center of our city.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6355 SET `male_text`='Astaia has fished up some curious treasures over the ages she has spent fishing.  Why don\'t you go see her over in the Tradesman\'s terrace and have her show you some of them.', `female_text`='Astaia has fished up some curious treasures over the ages she has spent fishing.  Why don\'t you go see her over in the Tradesman\'s terrace and have her show you some of them.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6356 SET `male_text`='Lysheana can offer you the proper documents, she resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeasten Darnassus.  May your fellowship bring glory to the Night Elves!', `female_text`='Lysheana can offer you the proper documents, she resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeasten Darnassus.  May your fellowship bring glory to the Night Elves!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6357 SET `male_text`='It is Vesprystus that you seek.  He watches over the hippogryphs that come and go from the base of Teldrassil.  You will find him through the portal in western Darnassus that will take you to Rut\'theran Village.', `female_text`='It is Vesprystus that you seek.  He watches over the hippogryphs that come and go from the base of Teldrassil.  You will find him through the portal in western Darnassus that will take you to Rut\'theran Village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6358 SET `male_text`='Jocaste was the greatest of Hunters of her time.  These days you can find her over in the Cenarion Enclave where she teaches those who are just starting down the Hunter\'s path.', `female_text`='Jocaste was the greatest of Hunters of her time.  These days you can find her over in the Cenarion Enclave where she teaches those who are just starting down the Hunter\'s path.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6359 SET `male_text`='Has the sun risen already?  There are just never enough hours in the night!  Well, Saelienne will take good care of you.  You can find her tending to her guests over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.', `female_text`='Has the sun risen already?  There are just never enough hours in the night!  Well, Saelienne will take good care of you.  You can find her tending to her guests over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.';
