UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6644 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hello young $g Master:Mistress;. I am Eva Sarkhoff and this is my husband, Lucien. It is a pleasure to make your acquaintance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6645 SET `male_text`='The pleasure is mine, madam. Might I ask what it is that you are doing here?', `female_text`='The pleasure is mine, madam. Might I ask what it is that you are doing here?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6646 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Certainly, $g sir:miss;. We were once servants of the house Barov: What is now known as the Scholomance.$B$BI was the head maid and Lucien was Master Barov\'s butler.$B$BWe had worked for the Barovs for decades, until...$B$B<Eva weeps.>';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6647 SET `male_text`='Until what, Eva? I must know.', `female_text`='Until what, Eva? I must know.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6648 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Oh it\'s just so horrible, $g sir:miss;. The house Barov was once full of life... full of splendor. The manor was the Barov\'s primary residence amidst their far reaching empire.$B$BLucien and I noticed that as the days progressed, the Barovs became depressed. Despondent. Paranoia and rage often overcame the master and missus. At night, we could hear the Barovs arguing in their chambers. From what we understood, their greed had \'broken the dam;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6649 SET `male_text`='What do you mean?', `female_text`='What do you mean?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6650 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='We suspect that in order to preserve their fortune and hold of the land - well past their lifespan - the Barovs made a deal with a powerful human mage named Kel\'Thuzad.$B$B<Eva shudders.>$B$BFrom this deal sprang the school of necromancy: A place which bore the Cult of the Damned and would become their capital.$B$BAs each week passed, the house Barov became more and more decrepit...$B$BDark beings began to take residence in the various wings of the house. Upkeep became impossible... and disgusting.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6651 SET `male_text`='Why didn\'t you just leave?', `female_text`='Why didn\'t you just leave?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6652 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='And go where? It was all that we knew; all that we had known and all that we would ever know.$B$BEventually, we lost contact with the Barovs and ultimately, were separated from the household. We knew not what happened to the other servants, only that there were screams. Tortured screams.$B$BKnowing that we had nowhere to go, Lucien and I were forced to hide in our quarters. During the day, when the school was relatively quiet, Lucien would sneak out to scrounge up food and drink.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6653 SET `male_text`='So what happened?', `female_text`='So what happened?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6654 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='We did this for about six months and watched as the house went through horrifying changes. Foul monsters roamed through the manor at will. Dark cultists populated every inch with various paraphernalia relating to rituals and sacrifices. We knew that we could not hide much longer.$B$BAs expected, we were found and captured. They stripped us of all our clothes and laid us out inside a circle of blood. We sat there for days, naked and terrified.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6655 SET `male_text`='No restraints? Just in a circle?', `female_text`='No restraints? Just in a circle?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6656 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Restraints? There are things in this world far more restraining than bars and shackles, young $g master:mistress;. The undead surrounded us, constantly tormenting us with horrifying acts of depravity.$B$BFinally, he came. He introduced himself as Doctor Theolen Krastinov. We came to know him as \'The Butcher.\'\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6657 SET `male_text`='Tell me more.', `female_text`='Tell me more.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6658 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='We finally understood what the screams were from. The Butcher exposed us to pain that we did not know existed. He used us in countless experiments, attempting to devise a plague.$B$BThe days turned to weeks. We would have died on the first day had it not been for that cruel bastard keeping us alive through magical means.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6659 SET `male_text`='This is an atrocity.', `female_text`='This is an atrocity.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6660 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='The Butcher would speak of \'the blood of innocents;
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6661 SET `male_text`='I feel sick.', `female_text`='I feel sick.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6662 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='We feel nothing. Our souls remain here, in limbo. We are unable to leave until our remains are found and spirits laid to rest.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6663 SET `male_text`='Ah, you must go to the great heights of Thunder Bluff to visit one of those.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village.  At the base of the bluffs is an elevator that will take you to the top.  When you get there ask for further directions from one of the Bluffwatchers.', `female_text`='Ah, you must go to the great heights of Thunder Bluff to visit one of those.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village.  At the base of the bluffs is an elevator that will take you to the top.  When you get there ask for further directions from one of the Bluffwatchers.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6664 SET `male_text`='How can I help?', `female_text`='How can I help?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6665 SET `male_text`='We have no such place in the village.  The soaring heights of Thunder Bluff does though.  Head north up the road out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the base of the bluffs.  There ride the elevator to the top and speak with a Bluffwatcher.  May your ancestors watch over you.', `female_text`='We have no such place in the village.  The soaring heights of Thunder Bluff does though.  Head north up the road out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the base of the bluffs.  There ride the elevator to the top and speak with a Bluffwatcher.  May your ancestors watch over you.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6666 SET `male_text`='There is a Wind Rider Master in the great city of Thunder Bluff to the north.  Ride the elevator from the base of Thunder Bluff to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for further instructions.', `female_text`='There is a Wind Rider Master in the great city of Thunder Bluff to the north.  Ride the elevator from the base of Thunder Bluff to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for further instructions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6667 SET `male_text`='Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions.', `female_text`='Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6668 SET `male_text`='Innkeeper Kauth can see to your needs.  He can be found on the west side of the village in one of the long houses.', `female_text`='Innkeeper Kauth can see to your needs.  He can be found on the west side of the village in one of the long houses.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6669 SET `male_text`='There is a time and a place for all things, including relaxation.  On the west side of Bloodhoof Village Innkeeper Kauth maintains a long house for those who seek to rest.  You will find him there.', `female_text`='There is a time and a place for all things, including relaxation.  On the west side of Bloodhoof Village Innkeeper Kauth maintains a long house for those who seek to rest.  You will find him there.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6670 SET `male_text`='It is Gennia Runetotem\'s counsel that you seek.  You will find her in the large tent on the east side of the village.', `female_text`='It is Gennia Runetotem\'s counsel that you seek.  You will find her in the large tent on the east side of the village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6671 SET `male_text`='The way of the Druid is sibling to the Shaman.  Gennia Runetotem is steeped in such knowledge.  Seek her out in the large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.', `female_text`='The way of the Druid is sibling to the Shaman.  Gennia Runetotem is steeped in such knowledge.  Seek her out in the large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6672 SET `male_text`='Yaw Sharpmane awaits you on the north edge of the village.  He can teach you the ways of the Hunter.', `female_text`='Yaw Sharpmane awaits you on the north edge of the village.  He can teach you the ways of the Hunter.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6673 SET `male_text`='To learn to be one with Nature in the eyes of the Earth Mother, this is a matter of pride.  If your will is to learn the ways of the Hunter you must seek out Yaw Sharpmane at the north end of Bloodhoof Village.', `female_text`='To learn to be one with Nature in the eyes of the Earth Mother, this is a matter of pride.  If your will is to learn the ways of the Hunter you must seek out Yaw Sharpmane at the north end of Bloodhoof Village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6674 SET `male_text`='There is a large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.  You will find Narm Skychaser awaiting you there.', `female_text`='There is a large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.  You will find Narm Skychaser awaiting you there.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6675 SET `male_text`='There is a wise one in the village who goes by the name Narm Skychaser.  He can continue your learning along the path of the Shaman.', `female_text`='There is a wise one in the village who goes by the name Narm Skychaser.  He can continue your learning along the path of the Shaman.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6676 SET `male_text`='Krang Stonehoof stands astride his training circle at the southeast corner of the village.', `female_text`='Krang Stonehoof stands astride his training circle at the southeast corner of the village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6677 SET `male_text`='If it is the way of the Warrior that you crave then you must seek out Krang Stonehoof.  You will find him in the southeast corner of the village at his training circle, often instructing his other students.', `female_text`='If it is the way of the Warrior that you crave then you must seek out Krang Stonehoof.  You will find him in the southeast corner of the village at his training circle, often instructing his other students.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6678 SET `male_text`='While we have no Alchemy Trainer here in Bloodhoof Village, there is one in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Follow the road there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions when you get to the top.', `female_text`='While we have no Alchemy Trainer here in Bloodhoof Village, there is one in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Follow the road there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions when you get to the top.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6679 SET `male_text`='Using the fruits of the Earth Mother to create potions to aid us in our eternal struggle is an honorable endeavor.  To learn of this you must travel north to our great home of Thunder Bluff.  When you arrive at the top seek out the assistance of one of the Bluffwatchers for more specific directions.', `female_text`='Using the fruits of the Earth Mother to create potions to aid us in our eternal struggle is an honorable endeavor.  To learn of this you must travel north to our great home of Thunder Bluff.  When you arrive at the top seek out the assistance of one of the Bluffwatchers for more specific directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6680 SET `male_text`='There is a Blacksmithing Trainer in our great home Thunder Bluff to the north.  If you seek such knowledge then head there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions.', `female_text`='There is a Blacksmithing Trainer in our great home Thunder Bluff to the north.  If you seek such knowledge then head there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6681 SET `male_text`='You desire to shape the bones of the Earth Mother into tools that will aid the Horde.  Good, good.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the elevator leading to the top of Thunder Bluff.  A Bluffwatcher there can give you further assistance.', `female_text`='You desire to shape the bones of the Earth Mother into tools that will aid the Horde.  Good, good.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the elevator leading to the top of Thunder Bluff.  A Bluffwatcher there can give you further assistance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6682 SET `male_text`='You will find Pyall Silentstride inside the great tent in the northwest corner of the village.  He can teach you what you crave.', `female_text`='You will find Pyall Silentstride inside the great tent in the northwest corner of the village.  He can teach you what you crave.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6683 SET `male_text`='My mouth waters just to think on it.  Pyall Silentstride is the finest cook in Bloodhoof Village.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.', `female_text`='My mouth waters just to think on it.  Pyall Silentstride is the finest cook in Bloodhoof Village.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6684 SET `male_text`='Away to Thunder Bluff to the north is where your journey takes you then friend.  Once there seek out the wisdom of one of the Bluffwatchers who can tell you directly where to find whom you seek.', `female_text`='Away to Thunder Bluff to the north is where your journey takes you then friend.  Once there seek out the wisdom of one of the Bluffwatchers who can tell you directly where to find whom you seek.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6685 SET `male_text`='Such wisdom is steeped in a mystery that can only be found in great Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to an elevator at the base of the bluffs.  Ride it to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for further assistance.', `female_text`='Such wisdom is steeped in a mystery that can only be found in great Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to an elevator at the base of the bluffs.  Ride it to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for further assistance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6686 SET `male_text`='Vira Younghoof keeps her practice inside the long house on the west side of the village.', `female_text`='Vira Younghoof keeps her practice inside the long house on the west side of the village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6687 SET `male_text`='Bandages, anti-venoms and such things, these are the inevitable necessities of life on the plains.  Vira Younghoof can teach you this knowledge.  You can find her in the long house on the west side of Bloodhoof Village.', `female_text`='Bandages, anti-venoms and such things, these are the inevitable necessities of life on the plains.  Vira Younghoof can teach you this knowledge.  You can find her in the long house on the west side of Bloodhoof Village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6688 SET `male_text`='You are looking for Uthan Stillwater.  You will find him west of the village, fishing at Stonebull Lake.', `female_text`='You are looking for Uthan Stillwater.  You will find him west of the village, fishing at Stonebull Lake.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6689 SET `male_text`='Give a bull a fish and feed him for a day.  Teach a bull to fish and feed him for life.  Uthan Stillwater can teach you how to fish.  Seek his wisdom west of Bloodhoof Village along the banks of Stonebull Lake.', `female_text`='Give a bull a fish and feed him for a day.  Teach a bull to fish and feed him for life.  Uthan Stillwater can teach you how to fish.  Seek his wisdom west of Bloodhoof Village along the banks of Stonebull Lake.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6690 SET `male_text`='If you desire to learn the ways of Herbalism then it is to Thunder Bluff that you must go.  Follow the road north out of Bloodhoof Village and take the elevator to the top of the rise.  You can ask a Bluffwatcher there for further assistance.', `female_text`='If you desire to learn the ways of Herbalism then it is to Thunder Bluff that you must go.  Follow the road north out of Bloodhoof Village and take the elevator to the top of the rise.  You can ask a Bluffwatcher there for further assistance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6691 SET `male_text`='There are those that would teach you of Herbalism in the great home of Thunder Bluff away to the north.  Follow the road out of the village to get there and at the base of the bluff ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  There are many Bluffwatchers there who can direct you further.', `female_text`='There are those that would teach you of Herbalism in the great home of Thunder Bluff away to the north.  Follow the road out of the village to get there and at the base of the bluff ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  There are many Bluffwatchers there who can direct you further.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6692 SET `male_text`='Inside the great tent at the northwest corner of the village is where Chaw Stronghide resides.  He will teach you what you must know of Leatherworking for now.', `female_text`='Inside the great tent at the northwest corner of the village is where Chaw Stronghide resides.  He will teach you what you must know of Leatherworking for now.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6693 SET `male_text`='When we use the hides of the animals we must fell for food or protection we give honor to the Earth Mother and respect to the animal.  Chaw Stronghide can teach you of such things.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.', `female_text`='When we use the hides of the animals we must fell for food or protection we give honor to the Earth Mother and respect to the animal.  Chaw Stronghide can teach you of such things.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6694 SET `male_text`='Hmmm, I think you will need to go up to Thunder Bluff to learn that.  Head north on the road out of Bloodhoof Village.  It will take you to the base of Thunder Bluff.  Ride the elevator to the top and you should be able to ask any of the Bluffwatchers there for further assistance.', `female_text`='Hmmm, I think you will need to go up to Thunder Bluff to learn that.  Head north on the road out of Bloodhoof Village.  It will take you to the base of Thunder Bluff.  Ride the elevator to the top and you should be able to ask any of the Bluffwatchers there for further assistance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6695 SET `male_text`='I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Take the road out of the village and when you get there ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  Any of the Bluffwatchers should be able to help you from there.', `female_text`='I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Take the road out of the village and when you get there ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  Any of the Bluffwatchers should be able to help you from there.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6696 SET `male_text`='Yonn Deepcut can be found inside the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.', `female_text`='Yonn Deepcut can be found inside the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6697 SET `male_text`='Ah yes, Skinning.  There is no one finer in wielding a skinning knife than Yonn Deepcut.  You can find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.', `female_text`='Ah yes, Skinning.  There is no one finer in wielding a skinning knife than Yonn Deepcut.  You can find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6698 SET `male_text`='Unfortunately we do not have one who teaches Tailoring here in Bloodhoof Village, but you can find a trainer in Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of the village until you come to a set of elevators.  Take one up to the top of the rise and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for directions.', `female_text`='Unfortunately we do not have one who teaches Tailoring here in Bloodhoof Village, but you can find a trainer in Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of the village until you come to a set of elevators.  Take one up to the top of the rise and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6699 SET `male_text`='Tailoring you say?  Hmmm.  Ah yes, of course.  You\'ll need to head to Thunder Bluff, up north.  Take the path out of the village to get there.  When you arrive at the base of the bluffs ride the elevator to the top of the rise and speak with one of the Bluffwatchers.', `female_text`='Tailoring you say?  Hmmm.  Ah yes, of course.  You\'ll need to head to Thunder Bluff, up north.  Take the path out of the village to get there.  When you arrive at the base of the bluffs ride the elevator to the top of the rise and speak with one of the Bluffwatchers.';
