UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6728 SET `male_text`='Can you help me with some directions?', `female_text`='Can you help me with some directions?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6729 SET `male_text`='We don\'t have a bank here in Brill, you\'ll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions.', `female_text`='We don\'t have a bank here in Brill, you\'ll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6730 SET `male_text`='What could you possibly need a bank for?  Very well, you\'ll need to go through the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  In the back are a set of elevators leading down into the Undercity.  When you get there stop any of those lumbering Abominations they like to call an Undercity Guardian and ask it for better directions.', `female_text`='What could you possibly need a bank for?  Very well, you\'ll need to go through the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  In the back are a set of elevators leading down into the Undercity.  When you get there stop any of those lumbering Abominations they like to call an Undercity Guardian and ask it for better directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6731 SET `male_text`='There\'s a Bat Handler inside the Undercity.  Head south down the road out of Brill, then west at the T-intersection.  The Ruins of Lordaeron will be on your left.  Go into them and then down into the Undercity.  You can ask an Undercity Guardian there for further assistance.', `female_text`='There\'s a Bat Handler inside the Undercity.  Head south down the road out of Brill, then west at the T-intersection.  The Ruins of Lordaeron will be on your left.  Go into them and then down into the Undercity.  You can ask an Undercity Guardian there for further assistance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6732 SET `male_text`='Somewhere to fly to?  You\'ll need to go to the Undercity for that!  Go south on the road out of town, then southwest to the Ruins of Lordaeron.  You can catch the elevator down to the Undercity from the back of the ruins and once there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions.', `female_text`='Somewhere to fly to?  You\'ll need to go to the Undercity for that!  Go south on the road out of town, then southwest to the Ruins of Lordaeron.  You can catch the elevator down to the Undercity from the back of the ruins and once there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6733 SET `male_text`='You\'ll find Innkeeper Renee inside the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of the street running through town.', `female_text`='You\'ll find Innkeeper Renee inside the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of the street running through town.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6734 SET `male_text`='Now if I were Innkeeper Renee where might I be?  Hmmm?  Oh, perhaps inside the Gallows\' End Tavern.  Yes, that\'s it, I\'m sure of it.  Try the southeast end of Brill... think you can find that?', `female_text`='Now if I were Innkeeper Renee where might I be?  Hmmm?  Oh, perhaps inside the Gallows\' End Tavern.  Yes, that\'s it, I\'m sure of it.  Try the southeast end of Brill... think you can find that?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6735 SET `male_text`='You\'ll find the Mage Trainer, Cain Firesong, upstairs on the landing at the Gallows\' End Tavern, which is on the southeast end of Brill.  I guess he checked in too late to get a room.', `female_text`='You\'ll find the Mage Trainer, Cain Firesong, upstairs on the landing at the Gallows\' End Tavern, which is on the southeast end of Brill.  I guess he checked in too late to get a room.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6736 SET `male_text`='Do I look to you like I cast spells?  Well, I did hear that Cain Firesong was hanging out on the upstairs landing of the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of town.  Odd how he just stands there outside of Gretchen\'s room like that.', `female_text`='Do I look to you like I cast spells?  Well, I did hear that Cain Firesong was hanging out on the upstairs landing of the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of town.  Odd how he just stands there outside of Gretchen\'s room like that.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6737 SET `male_text`='At the southeast edge of town is the Gallows\' End Tavern.  Go there and head upstairs, and you\'ll find Dark Cleric Beryl inside the reading room.', `female_text`='At the southeast edge of town is the Gallows\' End Tavern.  Go there and head upstairs, and you\'ll find Dark Cleric Beryl inside the reading room.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6738 SET `male_text`='Ah, you seek Dark Cleric Beryl.  He\'s upstairs in the reading room at the Gallows\' End Tavern.  Reading, praying, who knows what he\'s up to, and who would dare to ask?', `female_text`='Ah, you seek Dark Cleric Beryl.  He\'s upstairs in the reading room at the Gallows\' End Tavern.  Reading, praying, who knows what he\'s up to, and who would dare to ask?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6739 SET `male_text`='The Rogue Trainer\'s name is Marion Call.  You can find her upstairs in the reading room at the Gallows\' End Tavern at the town\'s southeast edge.', `female_text`='The Rogue Trainer\'s name is Marion Call.  You can find her upstairs in the reading room at the Gallows\' End Tavern at the town\'s southeast edge.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6740 SET `male_text`='Marion Call is keeping Dark Cleric Beryl company in the reading room upstairs at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast edge of Brill.  I\'m just dying to see who wins that staring contest.', `female_text`='Marion Call is keeping Dark Cleric Beryl company in the reading room upstairs at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast edge of Brill.  I\'m just dying to see who wins that staring contest.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6741 SET `male_text`='Rupert Boch is his name.  I hear that he\'s upstairs in one of the rooms at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast end of town.', `female_text`='Rupert Boch is his name.  I hear that he\'s upstairs in one of the rooms at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast end of town.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6742 SET `male_text`='That\'s Rupert Boch you\'re looking for.  He and his entourage have a room upstairs at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast end of Brill.', `female_text`='That\'s Rupert Boch you\'re looking for.  He and his entourage have a room upstairs at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast end of Brill.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6743 SET `male_text`='Look inside the Gallows\' End Tavern\'s main dining room for Austil de Mon.  The tavern is on the southeast edge of Brill.', `female_text`='Look inside the Gallows\' End Tavern\'s main dining room for Austil de Mon.  The tavern is on the southeast edge of Brill.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6744 SET `male_text`='Yeah, that would be Austil de Mon.  He\'s always hanging out in the tavern at the southeast end of town.  It\'s called the Gallows\' End Tavern, you can\'t miss it.', `female_text`='Yeah, that would be Austil de Mon.  He\'s always hanging out in the tavern at the southeast end of town.  It\'s called the Gallows\' End Tavern, you can\'t miss it.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6745 SET `male_text`='Our Alchemist\'s name is Carolai Anise.  You\'ll find her in a house at the northwest end of Brill.', `female_text`='Our Alchemist\'s name is Carolai Anise.  You\'ll find her in a house at the northwest end of Brill.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6746 SET `male_text`='You\'ll find Carolai Anise trying to blow up her house at the northwest end of town.  Why don\'t you go see if you can help her?', `female_text`='You\'ll find Carolai Anise trying to blow up her house at the northwest end of town.  Why don\'t you go see if you can help her?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6747 SET `male_text`='Sorry friend, we don\'t have one of those here in Brill.  You\'ll have to head to the Undercity for that.  The Undercity is underneath the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  From the back of the ruins take the elevator down and then speak to one of the Undercity Guardians to find your way further.', `female_text`='Sorry friend, we don\'t have one of those here in Brill.  You\'ll have to head to the Undercity for that.  The Undercity is underneath the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  From the back of the ruins take the elevator down and then speak to one of the Undercity Guardians to find your way further.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6748 SET `male_text`='Blacksmith?  Nope, our last one turned back into one of those mindless Scourge.  There\'s one in the Undercity though to the south of town though.  Undercity is underneath the Ruins of Lordaeron, clever name, huh?  Just take the elevators down at the back of the ruins and then you can talk to one of the Undercity Guardians.  They should be able to point you in the right direction.', `female_text`='Blacksmith?  Nope, our last one turned back into one of those mindless Scourge.  There\'s one in the Undercity though to the south of town though.  Undercity is underneath the Ruins of Lordaeron, clever name, huh?  Just take the elevators down at the back of the ruins and then you can talk to one of the Undercity Guardians.  They should be able to point you in the right direction.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6749 SET `male_text`='Fancy yourself a chef?  Head to the Undercity south of town for your training.  You can catch the elevators heading down at the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron.  Talk to one of those lumbering Undercity Guardians for further assistance once you arrive.', `female_text`='Fancy yourself a chef?  Head to the Undercity south of town for your training.  You can catch the elevators heading down at the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron.  Talk to one of those lumbering Undercity Guardians for further assistance once you arrive.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6750 SET `male_text`='Why cook when everything tastes like ashes in your mouth?  If you have one still that is.  Very well, head to the Undercity south of Brill and ask an Undercity Guardian there for further directions to their Cooking Trainer.  To get there you can take the elevators down from the rear of the Ruins of Lordaeron.', `female_text`='Why cook when everything tastes like ashes in your mouth?  If you have one still that is.  Very well, head to the Undercity south of Brill and ask an Undercity Guardian there for further directions to their Cooking Trainer.  To get there you can take the elevators down from the rear of the Ruins of Lordaeron.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6751 SET `male_text`='You can find Vance Undergloom upstairs in a room at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast side of Brill.', `female_text`='You can find Vance Undergloom upstairs in a room at the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast side of Brill.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6752 SET `male_text`='Word is that Vance Undergloom has taken a permanent room upstairs at the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of town.  I think he\'s just off the reading room.', `female_text`='Word is that Vance Undergloom has taken a permanent room upstairs at the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of town.  I think he\'s just off the reading room.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6753 SET `male_text`='While there\'s no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions.', `female_text`='While there\'s no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6754 SET `male_text`='Rifles, dynamite, bombs, exploding sheep... what\'s not to love?  To learn how to make these and many other exciting tools of the trade head to the Undercity, under the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  Take the elevators down at the back of the ruins.  Once you arrive speak to one of the Undercity Guardians about where the trainer is exactly.', `female_text`='Rifles, dynamite, bombs, exploding sheep... what\'s not to love?  To learn how to make these and many other exciting tools of the trade head to the Undercity, under the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  Take the elevators down at the back of the ruins.  Once you arrive speak to one of the Undercity Guardians about where the trainer is exactly.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6755 SET `male_text`='Nurse Neela greets all of her future customers as they enter the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of town.', `female_text`='Nurse Neela greets all of her future customers as they enter the Gallows\' End Tavern at the southeast end of town.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6756 SET `male_text`='Butcher you say?  Oh, First Aid Trainer!  Same thing.  When you see Nurse Neela standing just inside the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast side of town you\'ll know why.', `female_text`='Butcher you say?  Oh, First Aid Trainer!  Same thing.  When you see Nurse Neela standing just inside the Gallows\' End Tavern on the southeast side of town you\'ll know why.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6757 SET `male_text`='Clyde Kellen, the local bass master, has his favorite fishing spot just east of Brill at Brightwater Lake.', `female_text`='Clyde Kellen, the local bass master, has his favorite fishing spot just east of Brill at Brightwater Lake.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6758 SET `male_text`='Yeah, you\'ll always find Clyde Kellen fishing on the bank of Brightwater Lake just east of Brill.  Just watch out for psychos wearing masks while you\'re out there.  We had to shut down the kids\' summer camp last year.', `female_text`='Yeah, you\'ll always find Clyde Kellen fishing on the bank of Brightwater Lake just east of Brill.  Just watch out for psychos wearing masks while you\'re out there.  We had to shut down the kids\' summer camp last year.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6759 SET `male_text`='Look for Faruza.  Last I saw she was standing out front between the stables and the house on the northwest end of town.', `female_text`='Look for Faruza.  Last I saw she was standing out front between the stables and the house on the northwest end of town.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6760 SET `male_text`='Actually I prefer traditional medicines... leeches, maggots, bonesaws... that sort of thing.  Well to each their own.  You can find the our local Herbalism Trainer, Faruza, standing out front near the stables in Brill.', `female_text`='Actually I prefer traditional medicines... leeches, maggots, bonesaws... that sort of thing.  Well to each their own.  You can find the our local Herbalism Trainer, Faruza, standing out front near the stables in Brill.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6761 SET `male_text`='That would be Shelene Rhobart.  Take the road southeast out of Brill then head east at the intersection.  She\'s at a camp along the side of the road.', `female_text`='That would be Shelene Rhobart.  Take the road southeast out of Brill then head east at the intersection.  She\'s at a camp along the side of the road.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6762 SET `male_text`='Nothing quite like the feel of something dead rubbing up against you.  You can find Shelene Rhobart by heading southeast on the road out of town, and then going east at the intersection.  She\'s at a small camp there not too far along the road.', `female_text`='Nothing quite like the feel of something dead rubbing up against you.  You can find Shelene Rhobart by heading southeast on the road out of town, and then going east at the intersection.  She\'s at a small camp there not too far along the road.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6763 SET `male_text`='I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in the Undercity.  All you have to do to get there is head south out of town and go to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron.  Then take the elevator down into the Undercity itself and ask an Undercity Guardian for further directions.', `female_text`='I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in the Undercity.  All you have to do to get there is head south out of town and go to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron.  Then take the elevator down into the Undercity itself and ask an Undercity Guardian for further directions.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6764 SET `male_text`='I guess your first exercise is going to be to mine your way down to the Undercity.  Heh, get it?  Mine... nevermind.  To get to the Undercity go to the rear of the Ruins of Lordaeron south of Brill, and take the elevator down.  Ask one of the Undercity Guardians there for further assistance.', `female_text`='I guess your first exercise is going to be to mine your way down to the Undercity.  Heh, get it?  Mine... nevermind.  To get to the Undercity go to the rear of the Ruins of Lordaeron south of Brill, and take the elevator down.  Ask one of the Undercity Guardians there for further assistance.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6765 SET `male_text`='Rand Rhobart is fairly good at skinning felbats and the like.  You can find him at a camp along the road to the southeast of Brill.  Take the road southeast out of town and then head east at the intersection.', `female_text`='Rand Rhobart is fairly good at skinning felbats and the like.  You can find him at a camp along the road to the southeast of Brill.  Take the road southeast out of town and then head east at the intersection.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6766 SET `male_text`='You aiming to be a taxidermist?  I don\'t like people who think they can stuff and mount me because they think I\'m dead.  No?  Good!  Look for Rand Rhobart at a camp to the southeast of town.  To get to him take the road southeast out of Brill and hang a left at the intersection.', `female_text`='You aiming to be a taxidermist?  I don\'t like people who think they can stuff and mount me because they think I\'m dead.  No?  Good!  Look for Rand Rhobart at a camp to the southeast of town.  To get to him take the road southeast out of Brill and hang a left at the intersection.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6767 SET `male_text`='It is Bowen Brisboise that you seek then.  You\'ll find him inside his house southwest of Brill just on the other side of the bridge at Cold Hearth Manor.', `female_text`='It is Bowen Brisboise that you seek then.  You\'ll find him inside his house southwest of Brill just on the other side of the bridge at Cold Hearth Manor.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=6768 SET `male_text`='Black, grey and dark purple are the prescribed colors.  See to it that you don\'t stray onto the wrong side of fashion street friend.  Bowen Brisboise can help to see that you don\'t.  You\'ll find him inside Cold Hearth Manor on the other side of the bridge to the southwest of town.', `female_text`='Black, grey and dark purple are the prescribed colors.  See to it that you don\'t stray onto the wrong side of fashion street friend.  Bowen Brisboise can help to see that you don\'t.  You\'ll find him inside Cold Hearth Manor on the other side of the bridge to the southwest of town.';
