UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7438 SET `male_text`='The bear spirit looks upon you with a calm and peaceful gaze.  You hear a voice speak to you as though it was coming from the bear, but the creature makes no indication that it is speaking.$B$B\"Greetings, my young friend.  If you have come to me seeking guidance, then perhaps I can help you find what you seek.\"', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7439 SET `male_text`='What do you represent, spirit?', `female_text`='What do you represent, spirit?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7440 SET `male_text`='I represent the strength which bolsters you as a young druid.  I am the strength of the body, and the strength of the heart.  You have already come to know this in your training, and you draw upon this when you take on the aspect of the bear.$B$BContinue to keep the balance in all things, young one, and keep your perspective clear and true.  When you need me... I will be there for you.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7441 SET `male_text`='I represent the strength which bolsters you as a young druid.  You have come to me to learn this strength, young one, and I will teach this to you.  I will teach you all that is the spirit bear, provided you will listen and understand.$B$BIn order to know what it means to draw upon my spirit, you need to understand the importance of the strength of the body, as well as the strength of the heart.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7442 SET `male_text`='I seek to understand the importance of strength of the body.', `female_text`='I seek to understand the importance of strength of the body.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7443 SET `male_text`='Strength of the body is the power and swiftness of action.  You must keep yourself fit at all times, both physically and mentally.  The bear\'s girth highlights its strength, as it is a ferocious foe in combat.  The bear\'s girth, however, belies its lithe agility and sharp mind.  These are surprises you will use to your advantage.$B$BYou must rely on the strength of the bear\'s body in order to master the way of the Claw.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7444 SET `male_text`='I seek to understand the importance of strength of the heart.', `female_text`='I seek to understand the importance of strength of the heart.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7445 SET `male_text`='Strength of the heart is what gives you the resolve to take action... action that is rooted in intents that are pure and forthright.  To keep the balance is not to be complacent or banal.$B$BYou must show resolve for that which you believe in, and you must be willing to fight for it.  The mother bear shows endless conviction in protecting her young, as does an elder bear protecting his den.  It is this resolve, this strength of heart, which you must come to know if you are to master the way of the Claw.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7446 SET `male_text`='I have heard your words, Great Bear Spirit, and I understand.  I now seek your blessings to fully learn the way of the Claw.', `female_text`='I have heard your words, Great Bear Spirit, and I understand.  I now seek your blessings to fully learn the way of the Claw.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7447 SET `male_text`='It remains to be seen if you are ready, young one.  Even the wisest and oldest of druids are never truly ready when their ultimate time of testing comes.$B$BYou have heard my words, and now you must move on.  Heed what I have taught you.  There will be a time when you will have your strength tested.  You must face your foe as the bear would - with strength of body and with strength of heart.  Learn from the fight, young one.  Go... with my blessings.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7448 SET `male_text`='Greetings, $c.  You are welcome in Nighthaven, as well as all of Moonglade.  The Cenarion Circle welcomes all beings who respect the authority and command of nature.$B$BWhile you are here, please be sure to preserve the balance in all things.  Disturbances are not welcome here, and our wardens are trained to cease all hostilities without question.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7449 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Do you require an illusion?$B$BShould your illusion falter in the midst of your quest, return to me and I shall reapply the guise.$B$BShould you fail in your endeavors, do not give up! Return to me. I shall assist you until you have completed your objectives.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7450 SET `male_text`='Strive to keep the balance in all things, $c.  This is where true harmony lies.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=7451 SET `male_text`='Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to teach you.$B$BIt never hurts to reaffirm one\'s place within what I like to call the Great Balance.  As preservers of this balance, we must strive to continually keep our minds clear and our hearts strong.  Training helps us in this regard.', `female_text`='';
