UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9910 SET `male_text`='Blackfathom Deeps can be found at the north end of Zoram Strand along the coast of Ashenvale.', `female_text`='Blackfathom Deeps can be found at the north end of Zoram Strand along the coast of Ashenvale.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9911 SET `male_text`='Situated along the Zoram Strand of Ashenvale, Blackfathom Deeps was once a glorious temple dedicated to the night elves\' moon-goddess Elune. However, the great Sundering shattered the temple - sinking it beneath the waves of the Veiled Sea. There it remained untouched - until, drawn by its ancient power - the naga and satyr emerged to plumb its secrets. Legends hold that the ancient beast, Aku\'mai, has taken up residence within the temple\'s ruins. \n', `female_text`='Situated along the Zoram Strand of Ashenvale, Blackfathom Deeps was once a glorious temple dedicated to the night elves\' moon-goddess Elune. However, the great Sundering shattered the temple - sinking it beneath the waves of the Veiled Sea. There it remained untouched - until, drawn by its ancient power - the naga and satyr emerged to plumb its secrets. Legends hold that the ancient beast, Aku\'mai, has taken up residence within the temple\'s ruins. \n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9913 SET `male_text`='Gnomeregan can be found in western Dun Morogh.', `female_text`='Gnomeregan can be found in western Dun Morogh.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9914 SET `male_text`='Located in Dun Morogh, Gnomeregan has been the gnomes\' capital city for generations, though it was recently infested by mutant troggs. In a desperate attempt to retaliate, High Tinker Mekkatorque ordered the emergency venting of the city\'s radioactive waste tanks. Though the troggs became irradiated, their siege continued unabated and the gnomes were forced to seek refuge in the dwarven city of Ironforge, where the High Tinker now enlists brave souls to help his people reclaim their beloved city. \n', `female_text`='Located in Dun Morogh, Gnomeregan has been the gnomes\' capital city for generations, though it was recently infested by mutant troggs. In a desperate attempt to retaliate, High Tinker Mekkatorque ordered the emergency venting of the city\'s radioactive waste tanks. Though the troggs became irradiated, their siege continued unabated and the gnomes were forced to seek refuge in the dwarven city of Ironforge, where the High Tinker now enlists brave souls to help his people reclaim their beloved city. \n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9915 SET `male_text`='Razorfen Kraul', `female_text`='Razorfen Kraul';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9916 SET `male_text`='Razorfen Kraul can be found on the very southern tip of the Barrens on the west side of the road.', `female_text`='Razorfen Kraul can be found on the very southern tip of the Barrens on the west side of the road.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9917 SET `male_text`='During the War of the Ancients, the demigod Agamaggan came forth to battle the Burning Legion. The colossal boar was defeated, and over time in the areas where his blood fell, massive thorn-ridden vines sprouted to life. The quilboar came to occupy these regions and hold them sacred. The heart of these massive thorn-colonies is the Razorfen. Razorfen Kraul was conquered by the crone, Charlga Razorflank, who some speculate has been negotiating with agents of the Scourge for some insidious purpose.\n', `female_text`='During the War of the Ancients, the demigod Agamaggan came forth to battle the Burning Legion. The colossal boar was defeated, and over time in the areas where his blood fell, massive thorn-ridden vines sprouted to life. The quilboar came to occupy these regions and hold them sacred. The heart of these massive thorn-colonies is the Razorfen. Razorfen Kraul was conquered by the crone, Charlga Razorflank, who some speculate has been negotiating with agents of the Scourge for some insidious purpose.\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9918 SET `male_text`='Scarlet Monastery', `female_text`='Scarlet Monastery';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9919 SET `male_text`='Scarlet Monastery lies in the hills northeast of Tirisfal Glades.', `female_text`='Scarlet Monastery lies in the hills northeast of Tirisfal Glades.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9920 SET `male_text`='The monastery was once a center for learning and enlightenment. With the rise of the undead Scourge during the Third War, the peaceful Monastery was converted into a stronghold of the fanatical Scarlet Crusade. The Crusaders are intolerant of all non-human races, regardless of alliance or affiliation. They believe that any and all outsiders are potential carriers of the undead plague - and must be destroyed. \n', `female_text`='The monastery was once a center for learning and enlightenment. With the rise of the undead Scourge during the Third War, the peaceful Monastery was converted into a stronghold of the fanatical Scarlet Crusade. The Crusaders are intolerant of all non-human races, regardless of alliance or affiliation. They believe that any and all outsiders are potential carriers of the undead plague - and must be destroyed. \n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9921 SET `male_text`='Razorfen Downs', `female_text`='Razorfen Downs';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9922 SET `male_text`='Razorfen Downs can be found on the very southern tip of the Barrens on the east side of the road.', `female_text`='Razorfen Downs can be found on the very southern tip of the Barrens on the east side of the road.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9923 SET `male_text`='Crafted from the same vines as Razorfen Kraul, Razorfen Downs is the traditional capital city of the quilboar race. The sprawling, thorn-ridden labyrinth houses a veritable army of loyal quilboar as well as their high priests - the Death\'s Head tribe. Recently, however, a looming shadow has fallen over the crude den. Agents of the undead Scourge - led by the lich, Amnennar the Coldbringer - have taken control over the quilboar race and turned the maze of thorns into a bastion of undead might. \n\n', `female_text`='Crafted from the same vines as Razorfen Kraul, Razorfen Downs is the traditional capital city of the quilboar race. The sprawling, thorn-ridden labyrinth houses a veritable army of loyal quilboar as well as their high priests - the Death\'s Head tribe. Recently, however, a looming shadow has fallen over the crude den. Agents of the undead Scourge - led by the lich, Amnennar the Coldbringer - have taken control over the quilboar race and turned the maze of thorns into a bastion of undead might. \n\n';
