UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9927 SET `male_text`='Uldaman is an ancient Titan vault that has laid buried within the earth since the world\'s creation. Dwarven excavations of the city have recently released the Titans\' first failed creations: the troggs. Legends say that when the Titans deemed the trogg experiment a failure they tried again, resulting in the creation of the dwarven race. These secrets are recorded on the fabled Discs of Norgannon - massive artifacts that lie at the bottom of the ancient city, protected by giant constructs of living stone. \r\n', `female_text`='Uldaman is an ancient Titan vault that has laid buried within the earth since the world\'s creation. Dwarven excavations of the city have recently released the Titans\' first failed creations: the troggs. Legends say that when the Titans deemed the trogg experiment a failure they tried again, resulting in the creation of the dwarven race. These secrets are recorded on the fabled Discs of Norgannon - massive artifacts that lie at the bottom of the ancient city, protected by giant constructs of living stone. \r\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9928 SET `male_text`='Zul\'Farrak', `female_text`='Zul\'Farrak';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9929 SET `male_text`='The ruins of Zul\'Farrak are located in the northwestern corner of the Tanaris Desert.', `female_text`='The ruins of Zul\'Farrak are located in the northwestern corner of the Tanaris Desert.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9930 SET `male_text`='This sun-blasted city is home to the Sandfury trolls, known for their particular ruthlessness and dark mysticism. Troll legends tell of a powerful sword called Sul\'thraze the Lasher, a weapon capable of instilling fear and weakness in even the most formidable of foes. Long ago, the weapon was split in half. However, rumors have circulated that the two halves may be found somewhere within Zul\'Farrak\'s walls.\n', `female_text`='This sun-blasted city is home to the Sandfury trolls, known for their particular ruthlessness and dark mysticism. Troll legends tell of a powerful sword called Sul\'thraze the Lasher, a weapon capable of instilling fear and weakness in even the most formidable of foes. Long ago, the weapon was split in half. However, rumors have circulated that the two halves may be found somewhere within Zul\'Farrak\'s walls.\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9931 SET `male_text`='Maraudon', `female_text`='Maraudon';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9932 SET `male_text`='Maraudon is located in the middle of the western coast of Desolace, in the Valley of Spears.', `female_text`='Maraudon is located in the middle of the western coast of Desolace, in the Valley of Spears.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9933 SET `male_text`='Maraudon is one of the most sacred sites within Desolace. The great temple/cavern is the burial place of Zaetar, one of two immortal sons born to the demigod, Cenarius. Legend holds that Zaetar and the earth elemental princess, Theradras, sired the misbegotten centaur race. It is said that upon their emergence, the barbaric centaur turned on their father and killed him. Some believe that Theradras, in her grief, trapped Zaetar\'s spirit within the winding cavern - used its energies for some malign purpose. ', `female_text`='Maraudon is one of the most sacred sites within Desolace. The great temple/cavern is the burial place of Zaetar, one of two immortal sons born to the demigod, Cenarius. Legend holds that Zaetar and the earth elemental princess, Theradras, sired the misbegotten centaur race. It is said that upon their emergence, the barbaric centaur turned on their father and killed him. Some believe that Theradras, in her grief, trapped Zaetar\'s spirit within the winding cavern - used its energies for some malign purpose. ';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9934 SET `male_text`='Sunken Temple', `female_text`='Sunken Temple';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9935 SET `male_text`='The Sunken Temple can be found in the center of a great lake in eastern Swamp of Sorrows.', `female_text`='The Sunken Temple can be found in the center of a great lake in eastern Swamp of Sorrows.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9936 SET `male_text`='Over a thousand years ago a group of troll priests known as the Atal\'ai attempted to bring back an ancient blood god named Hakkar the Soulflayer. After the resulting civil war the priests were defeated and exiled to the Swamp of Sorrows. There they erected a temple to Hakkar to prepare for his arrival into the physical world. The dragon Aspect Ysera soon learned of the Atal\'ai\'s plans and smashed the temple beneath the marshes. To this day, the temple\'s ruins are guarded by the mighty green dragons.\n', `female_text`='Over a thousand years ago a group of troll priests known as the Atal\'ai attempted to bring back an ancient blood god named Hakkar the Soulflayer. After the resulting civil war the priests were defeated and exiled to the Swamp of Sorrows. There they erected a temple to Hakkar to prepare for his arrival into the physical world. The dragon Aspect Ysera soon learned of the Atal\'ai\'s plans and smashed the temple beneath the marshes. To this day, the temple\'s ruins are guarded by the mighty green dragons.\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9937 SET `male_text`='Blackrock Depths', `female_text`='Blackrock Depths';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9938 SET `male_text`='Blackrock Mountain lies between Searing Gorge in the north and Burning Steppes in the south.', `female_text`='Blackrock Mountain lies between Searing Gorge in the north and Burning Steppes in the south.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9939 SET `male_text`='Once the capital city of the Dark Iron dwarves, this volcanic labyrinth now serves as the seat of power for Ragnaros the Firelord. Ragnaros has uncovered the secret to creating life from stone and plans to build an army of unstoppable golems to aid him in conquering the whole of Blackrock Mountain. Obsessed with defeating Nefarian and his draconic minions, Ragnaros will go to any extreme to achieve final victory.  \n', `female_text`='Once the capital city of the Dark Iron dwarves, this volcanic labyrinth now serves as the seat of power for Ragnaros the Firelord. Ragnaros has uncovered the secret to creating life from stone and plans to build an army of unstoppable golems to aid him in conquering the whole of Blackrock Mountain. Obsessed with defeating Nefarian and his draconic minions, Ragnaros will go to any extreme to achieve final victory.  \n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9940 SET `male_text`='Blackrock Spire', `female_text`='Blackrock Spire';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=9941 SET `male_text`='The mighty fortress carved within the fiery bowels of Blackrock Mountain was held by the sinister Dark Iron dwarves for centuries until Nefarian - the cunning son of the dragon, Deathwing - took control of the upper Spire and made war on the dwarves\' holdings in the mountain\'s volcanic depths. Realizing that the dwarves were led by the mighty fire elemental, Ragnaros - Nefarian vowed to crush his enemies and claim the whole of Blackrock mountain for himself. \n', `female_text`='The mighty fortress carved within the fiery bowels of Blackrock Mountain was held by the sinister Dark Iron dwarves for centuries until Nefarian - the cunning son of the dragon, Deathwing - took control of the upper Spire and made war on the dwarves\' holdings in the mountain\'s volcanic depths. Realizing that the dwarves were led by the mighty fire elemental, Ragnaros - Nefarian vowed to crush his enemies and claim the whole of Blackrock mountain for himself. \n';
