UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10712 SET `male_text`='Hello, Rutgar. The Commander has sent me here to gather some information about his missing wife.', `female_text`='Hello, Rutgar. The Commander has sent me here to gather some information about his missing wife.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10713 SET `male_text`='You best have a seat then, this is gonna be a long one.$B$BWhen we initially arrived in Silithus, Mistress Mar\'alith was the first of the night elves from Cenarion Hold to join the expedition. Our routine was nothing out of the ordinary: Form a party to venture into the various hives and search for lost artifacts. ', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10714 SET `male_text`='That sounds dangerous.', `female_text`='That sounds dangerous.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10715 SET `male_text`='It sure is! Those hives were abuzz with various silithid that were none too happy to see us.$B$BEverything was going fine until we came across a glyphed crystal in Hive\'Regal. She was drawn to it like a moth to a flame! She put her pretty little cheek up against the crystal and instantly entered a trance-like state. Naturally, this worried my crew. We picked her up and carried her out of there with a quickness!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10716 SET `male_text`='What happened to her after that?', `female_text`='What happened to her after that?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10717 SET `male_text`='We took her to the Commander with hopes that the druids of the Circle could fix her up. Sure enough, they were able to wake her up. We figured our business with the Circle was done and we could get back to work.$B$BA few weeks passed and everything was going fine. Brann was still around back then so we had a bit of order in our work structure. Then one day, out of the blue, she appeared back at our camp.\n', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10718 SET `male_text`='Natalia?', `female_text`='Natalia?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10719 SET `male_text`='Are you daft? Who else would I be talking about? Yes, the girl - Mistress Mar\'alith. Anyhow, she was back and not in too good of a mood. That\'s when the demands started flowing.\n', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10720 SET `male_text`='What demands?', `female_text`='What demands?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10721 SET `male_text`='She demanded that we immediately head back to Hive\'Regal! Brann would have none of that sass. He told her that there\'s no way we would go back into those hives without an army backing us up. It had gotten far too dangerous. The number of those stinking insects seemed to have tripled from when we first ventured into \'em.$B$BThat\'s when Natalia lost it!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10722 SET `male_text`='Lost it? What do you mean?', `female_text`='Lost it? What do you mean?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10723 SET `male_text`='What do you mean what do I mean? She went nutso! The girl went straight crazy on us. Now ordinarily I don\'t hit girls but after I recovered from the blackout, I was pretty damned angry. Brann, Rutgar, me and the monkey went positively orc on her! It\'s a miracle we were able to fend her off. She seemed almost possessed!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10724 SET `male_text`='Possessed by what?', `female_text`='Possessed by what?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10725 SET `male_text`='Who knows? Anyhow, that was the last I saw of her. Maybe Frankal can give you better information.$B$BNot to steer off topic here as I\'m sure the work you\'re doing for the Commander is important, but we\'re onto something huge here. HUGE! Our requests to Ironforge for an army have so far fallen on deaf ears. Apparently we\'re stretched too thin in protecting the realm or some such nonsense. Once you take your report back to the Commander, come back down here with some friends. We need your help!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10726 SET `male_text`='I\'ll be back once I straighten this mess out.', `female_text`='I\'ll be back once I straighten this mess out.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10727 SET `male_text`='Hello, Frankal. I\'ve heard that you might have some information as to the whereabouts of Mistress Natalia Mar\'alith.', `female_text`='Hello, Frankal. I\'ve heard that you might have some information as to the whereabouts of Mistress Natalia Mar\'alith.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10728 SET `male_text`='Oh brother, not this again... Have a seat $g sonny:missy;.$B$BI\'m sure Rutgar has told you some of this story already so I\'ll spare you the boring details and get right down to the nitty gritty.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10729 SET `male_text`='That\'s what I like to hear.', `female_text`='That\'s what I like to hear.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10730 SET `male_text`='Right then! So the Mistress had come back for a second go at the hives but Brann was having none of that nonsense! Before the melee began, she started talking to something or someone. Crazier still, she started chanting in a language none of us had ever heard.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10731 SET `male_text`='That\'s odd.', `female_text`='That\'s odd.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10732 SET `male_text`='You\'re telling me! It\'s even stranger considering between Brann, Rutgar, me and the monkey, we know 38 different languages including a touch of Titan - both Vanir and Aesir.$B$BSo anyway, whatever she was click clacking about, it definitely wasn\'t with anyone \"present.\" She then nodded and went on the offensive! Attacked us outright!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10733 SET `male_text`='You couldn\'t handle a lone night elf priestess?', `female_text`='You couldn\'t handle a lone night elf priestess?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10734 SET `male_text`='Listen $g sonny:missy;, I\'ll have you know that whatever attacked us was no priestess of nothin\'! Her eyes were aglow with something evil and she was genuinely frothing at the mouth! She came in, did some kind of crazy scream that sent us all runnin\' in separate directions then started flayin\' our minds one by one. I\'d be hearin\' shadowy words in my head, watchin\' the other\'s periodically black out here and there. It was madness! We would have been done for if not for the damned monkey.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10735 SET `male_text`='I\'ve been meaning to ask you about that monkey.', `female_text`='I\'ve been meaning to ask you about that monkey.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10736 SET `male_text`='What\'s there to ask? He\'s a monkey you crazy fool. Anyhow, so yea, the monkey went into a frenzy after seein\' ol\' Brann flop into the sand face first. Nothin\' the night elf could do was stopping Glibb here from poundin\' on her noggin.', `female_text`='';
