UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10771 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='I\'ve come back to my old home so my knowledge may be passed on.  Unlike the mindless undead around me, I\'ve chosen this unlife for my own reasons.$B$BThe silithid are formidable opponents, $n.  I\'ve learned to respect them as much as I despise them.$B$BMuch of their deadliness comes from the strength and lightness of their chitin, which I\'ve learned to work into armor.  As we seem to have a common enemy I shall teach you my trade. ';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10772 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hello $c, and welcome to the Darkmoon Faire. There is so much to do here at the faire that it can be a little overwhelming for our first time visitors. That\'s why I\'m here to help. Do you have any questions?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10773 SET `male_text`='What can I purchase?', `female_text`='What can I purchase?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10774 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='An excellent question! We have many things for sale here at the faire. If you are interested in food and drink, then head over to Stamp and Sylannia\'s booth. My favorite is the Darkmoon Special Reserve.\n\nIf you\'d rather purchase something more exotic, then Lhara may have just the thing for you. She specializes in rarities from all over the world.\n\nAnd then there is Flik running around here somewhere. If you can grab him he sells balls for throwing and frogs to keep as pets.\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10775 SET `male_text`='What are Darkmoon Faire Prize Tickets and how do I get them?', `female_text`='What are Darkmoon Faire Prize Tickets and how do I get them?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10776 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Glad you asked. Darkmoon Faire Prize Tickets are our way of letting you help with the faire, and in return you can turn in your tickets for special prizes!\n\nTo get started you\'ll want to talk to Chronos, Kerri Hicks, Ringling and Yebb Nebblegear to see who you can best help. They always have something that needs doing to improve and expand our attractions.\n\nThen when you have enough tickets, speak with Gelvas Grimegate and he will give you a list of prizes to choose from.\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10777 SET `male_text`='What are Darkmoon Cards?', `female_text`='What are Darkmoon Cards?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10778 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='No one really knows who made the Darkmoon Cards or what their true purpose is, but I can tell you that they have been found all over Azeroth, usually in the hands of a villain attempting to unlock their mysteries.\n\nThere are four types of Darkmoon Cards; Beasts, Elementals, Portals and Warlords, with eight cards, Ace to Eight in each suit. If you collect all eight of one suit then you can turn them into a deck that you can give to our Professor Thaddeus Paleo in exchange for a powerful trinket.\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10779 SET `male_text`='What other things can I do at the faire?', `female_text`='What other things can I do at the faire?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10780 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='I highly recommend that you visit Sayge to get your fortune told. I know, I know... he\'s a gnoll.  But he\'s a very special gnoll with the power to divine your future!$B$BAnd we are constantly expanding the faire with all manner of new attractions!';
