UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10976 SET `male_text`='Captain!  Lieutenant Stouthammer requests your presence!  The enemy is approaching, sir!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10977 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hello, how are you feeling today, $c? Well, I hope. You may be wondering what is going on here. There\'s a war at Ahn\'Qiraj that is being planned and prepared for. We and the Horde are preparing as best we can for it.$B$BTo that end, the Alliance has asked me to supervise the collection of silk bandages here. To date we\'ve managed to put together $2082w out of $2083w needed. Are you thinking about helping out?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10978 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='That\'s very kind of you to ask, but it would appear that we\'ve collected all of the silk bandages that we\'ll need. You could ask around though and see if anyone else needs help with their collections.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10979 SET `male_text`='$C, even our hardiest warriors and scouts will need use of the healing arts in the war to come at Ahn\'Qiraj. And when there is no magical healing available, they must rely upon our efforts here.$B$BTo date I have collected $2088w runecloth bandages, out of $2090w needed. If you are willing, we should speak further on how you can do your part.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10980 SET `male_text`='$C, through the efforts of many we have managed to gather up all of the runecloth bandages that the Alliance feels it needs for the upcoming conflict. Were I you, I would ask some of the others here to see if they still have collection tasks that need fulfilling.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10982 SET `male_text`='Stand ready!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10983 SET `male_text`='Mmm, mmm, mmm. Can you smell that?! That\'s good eatin\' right there, $c. Rainbow Fin Albacore hits the spot every time. Slicky Gastronome here, ace connoisseur of all things edible, especially fish. With the Ahn\'Qiraj War looming, the Alliance thought it wise to bring in an expert for the war effort, so here I am, large and in charge.$B$BLooks like we\'re going to need $2093w of the fish, and we\'ve got a pile that currently comes to $2092w.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10984 SET `male_text`='Well, looks like we have all of the cooked albacore that we can properly salt and store for the upcoming war at Ahn\'Qiraj. Thanks for asking though, $c. If you have a mind to, check around with the other collectors. I\'d bet there\'s someone else here that could use your help with gathering up whatever it is that they need.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10988 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Oh, hi, $c. I guess the Alliance asked me to come here and keep track of all of this cooked meat that people are gathering because of the impending doom at Ahn\'Qiraj. Doesn\'t that sound like fun?$B$BAnyway, I suppose you\'d like to know how much we have. Last time I counted it we were at $2098w out of a total $2099w roast raptor needed.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10989 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Looks like you\'re too late, $c. We have all of the roast raptor that we need; killed, cooked and salted. Anyway, it looks like some of the others around here could use some help. You should go check with them. I\'m going to see if they\'ll let me go home now.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10990 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Proper sustenance will keep a soldier alive long after the wounds of the battlefield should have finished $g him : her; off, $c. If we\'re to persevere in the Ahn\'Qiraj War to come, we\'ll need all of the provisions that we can carry. I\'m gathering up spotted yellowtail fish at this location before it is to be shipped out.$B$BAs of now we have $2101w, but we need to collect a total of $2103w if we\'re going to be able to feed everyone.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10991 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Thank you for your inquiry, $c, but we have all of the spotted yellowtail necessary. There are others here though that may still be gathering materiel for the upcoming war. Seek them out, and may the goddess shine upon you.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10995 SET `male_text`='Hello, $c. I\'m sure that I don\'t need to inform you of the gravity of our situation here. We need to gather many goods, and in most cases assemble them into materiel, to be transported to Cenarion Hold in Silithus. This is no small effort.$B$BRecently in the Molten Core we discovered something called a singed corestone. Our blacksmiths and engineers tell us that they can put them to good use, so I\'m supervising their accumulation here. As of now, out of $2110w needed, we\'ve managed to collect $2108w.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10996 SET `male_text`='Thanks to the combined efforts of the Alliance\'s adventuring guilds, we have been able to gather all of the singed corestones we think that we\'ll need. However, you might want to check around with the other collectors here to see if they still need help in gathering up vital resources.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10997 SET `male_text`='We need a great number of copper bars, $c. The upcoming war at Ahn\'Qiraj is going to use up a lot of metal for weapons, armor and whatnot. I\'m told that the Horde alone needs to collect $1998w copper bars. As of now we have $2018w.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=10998 SET `male_text`='According to the latest count we have all of the copper bars we\'re going to need for the war. If I were you I\'d check with some of the other collectors here to see if they need your help.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11001 SET `male_text`='Throm\'ka, $c. You are here to help me with tin bars? They tell me that I will need $2006w so that they can make weapons and armor for the upcoming Ahn\'Qiraj War, but I only have $2005w right now. You are going to bring me more!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11002 SET `male_text`='No more tin bars! Even my arms hurt from stacking them. We have all that we need, so go ask one of the others if they need you to collect anything.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11005 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hail, $c.  The Ironforge Brigade is stationed here to keep an eye on Hive\'Zora.  The Cenarion Circle druids have been monitoring silithid movement and they\'re anticipating something major in this area.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11006 SET `male_text`='I\'m here to aid the Captain.', `female_text`='I\'m here to aid the Captain.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11007 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='The Captain is busy at the moment.  He\'s studying maps we recently acquired of the underground silithid hives.  Stay with us if you\'d like to help, he\'ll come out any moment now.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11008 SET `male_text`='%s is stunned by Elune\'s Candle!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11009 SET `male_text`='Kill $n!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11010 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hey mon, you be here ta bring me mithril bars no doubt. There be big trouble brewin\' in the Silithus desert at Ahn\'Qiraj. We and the Alliance goin\' all out this time to stop them bugs, and that be why you seein\' everyone here.$B$BThe Horde be askin\' me to collect $2009w for the war effort, but I only have $2008w. So ya gonna help me out, or what?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11011 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Yah, I know, it be lookin\' like we already have all of the mithril bars we be needin\' for the war. But ya know, there still be plenty of folk \'round here that can probably be usin\' your help right about now.  Thanks mon.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11012 SET `male_text`='They come now. Try not to get yourself killed, young blood.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11013 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hello, young $c. Are you here to bring me a batch of peacebloom? We are collecting them to make potions and elixirs for the Ahn\'Qiraj war effort. Though tragic that we are forced into this war, the results will be even more terrible if we do not prepare properly.$B$BThe Horde has tasked me with the collection of $2020w peacebloom, and so far we\'ve managed to put together $2021w. If you have it within your ability, please gather up all that you can and return them to me here.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11014 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='It is good that you wish to help, $c. Unfortunately I have collected up all of the peacebloom that we feel we\'ll need for the war effort. Maybe you could ask around; I\'m sure that there are likely to be others here that still need your aid in gathering other things.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11015 SET `male_text`='You seek to harm me, $r?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11016 SET `male_text`='I am a treasure hunter in search of powerful artifacts. Give them to me and you will not be harmed.', `female_text`='I am a treasure hunter in search of powerful artifacts. Give them to me and you will not be harmed.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11017 SET `male_text`='You challenge the charge of the Blue Dragonflight? DIE, vermin.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11018 SET `male_text`='%s counterattacks with retaliation.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11022 SET `male_text`='My watch is eternal, mortal.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11025 SET `male_text`='<Andorov looks at you grimly.>$B$BIf it bleeds, we can kill it.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11026 SET `male_text`='Let\'s find out.', `female_text`='Let\'s find out.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11027 SET `male_text`='Your world shall suffer an unmerciful end. The Nightmare comes for you!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11028 SET `male_text`='Remember, Rajaxx, when I said I\'d kill you last?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11029 SET `male_text`='The end rapidly approaches! Surrender yourselves to Eranikus and be spared eternal suffering!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11030 SET `male_text`='Pitiful, predictable mortals... You know not what you have done! The Master\'s will fulfilled. The Moonglade shall be destroyed and Malfurion along with it!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11031 SET `male_text`='Run, little ones. Run and tell your masters that Eranikus has come to raze their world.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11032 SET `male_text`='Kill first, ask questions later... Incoming!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11033 SET `male_text`='You seek the scepter shard charged to the protection of the Blue Flight?$B$B<Azuregos appears to be smiling.>', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11034 SET `male_text`='How did you know? I mean, yes... Yes I am looking for that shard. Do you have it?', `female_text`='How did you know? I mean, yes... Yes I am looking for that shard. Do you have it?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11035 SET `male_text`='Of course I do not have the shard. That would be asinine. I walk amongst savages in this cursed land! I cannot take five steps without some crazed orc or human trying to thrust a sharp stick into my hide. At any given time you could very well be speaking to my ghostly spirit.$B$BAnyhow... I hid it.$B$BGo on... ask me where.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11036 SET `male_text`='Alright. Where?', `female_text`='Alright. Where?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11037 SET `male_text`='You are going to love this story, $r. See, here is the thing. As soon as Malygos charged me with protecting the scepter shard, I knew I was in for an eternity of headache and pain.$B$BAll I want to do is study these magic rich shorelines and take in what artifacts might remain from the Sundering. You know, there was once a thriving Highborne civilization here! You don\'t have to tell me that there is going to be some solid magical items around here, $r. I can smell it!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11038 SET `male_text`='By Bronzbeard\'s... um, beard! What are you talking about?', `female_text`='By Bronzbeard\'s... um, beard! What are you talking about?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11039 SET `male_text`='As I was saying, I held onto that scepter shard for a good five-hundred years and it was nothing but trouble. It attracted all kinds of attention - the wrong kind of attention. I want to be left alone to my studies not babysit some would be hero\'s ticket to glory. So... I gave it to the fish.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11040 SET `male_text`='Fish? You gave a piece of what could be the key to saving all life on Kalimdor to a fish?', `female_text`='Fish? You gave a piece of what could be the key to saving all life on Kalimdor to a fish?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11041 SET `male_text`='Not just any fish, mortal. This fish was a minnow. A very special minnow.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11042 SET `male_text`='A minnow? The oceans are filled with minnows! There could be a hundred million minnows out there!', `female_text`='A minnow? The oceans are filled with minnows! There could be a hundred million minnows out there!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11043 SET `male_text`='Exactly!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11044 SET `male_text`='...', `female_text`='...';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11045 SET `male_text`='Genius, I know... It will never be found; but, in case it is found, I gave the minnow some special powers.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11046 SET `male_text`='You put the piece on a minnow and placed the minnow somewhere in the waters of the sea between here and the Eastern Kingdoms? And this minnow has special powers?', `female_text`='You put the piece on a minnow and placed the minnow somewhere in the waters of the sea between here and the Eastern Kingdoms? And this minnow has special powers?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11047 SET `male_text`='Correct. You\'ve been listening! This minnow is really quite a terrible creature of my own creation. When I am relaxing I like to think of the unlucky fishermen who have run into this minnow and been devoured whole. I bet they were quite surprised!$B$B<Azuregos laughs.>', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11048 SET `male_text`='You\'re insane.', `female_text`='You\'re insane.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11049 SET `male_text`='Genius is often misunderstood, $r. Now, about the scepter shard... If you want that shard and do not wish to spend the next ten thousand years searching for it, you are going to have to listen very carefully.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11050 SET `male_text`='I\'m all ears.', `female_text`='I\'m all ears.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11051 SET `male_text`='Two words: Arcanite buoy.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11052 SET `male_text`='Come again.', `female_text`='Come again.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11053 SET `male_text`='Right then... You have to build an arcanite buoy and place it in the ocean. My minnow will be attracted to the magical emanations. When he gets near the buoy - BLAMO! It will explode in a glorious pulse of arcane energy, revealing the minnow\'s true form. Also, you may or may not incur the wrath of Neptulon. A 50/50 chance I would say.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11054 SET `male_text`='Ok, let me get this straight. You put the scepter shard entrusted to your Flight by Anachronos on a minnow of your own making and now you expect me to build an... an arcanite buoy or something... to force your minnow out of hiding? AND potentially incur the wrath of an Elemental Lord? Did I miss anything? Perhaps I am to do this without any clothes on, during a solar eclipse, on a leap year?\n', `female_text`='Ok, let me get this straight. You put the scepter shard entrusted to your Flight by Anachronos on a minnow of your own making and now you expect me to build an... an arcanite buoy or something... to force your minnow out of hiding? AND potentially incur the wrath of an Elemental Lord? Did I miss anything? Perhaps I am to do this without any clothes on, during a solar eclipse, on a leap year?\n';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11055 SET `male_text`='General Rajaxx has been owned. Chalk up another victory for Andorov.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11056 SET `male_text`='If I did not know better I would think that you were mocking me, mortal; but yes, that is mostly correct. You may remain fully clothed.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11057 SET `male_text`='FINE! And how, dare I ask, am I supposed to acquire an arcanite buoy?', `female_text`='FINE! And how, dare I ask, am I supposed to acquire an arcanite buoy?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11058 SET `male_text`='Take this ledger to an old acquaintance of mine in Tanaris. His name is Narain Soothfancy - terrible, terrible, psychic but an amazing engineer! He should be able to make sense of it all.$B$BNo need to thank me, $n. It\'s the least I could do.$B$BGood day!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11059 SET `male_text`='But...', `female_text`='But...';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11060 SET `male_text`='I SAID GOOD DAY!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11061 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Step carefully mortal.  You tread where mightier beings have met their fate.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11062 SET `male_text`='A thousand years ago, when the War of the Shifting Sands ended, three of our kin sacrificed themselves and held the Qiraji inside these halls while Anachronos and Staghelm sealed Ahn\'Qiraj shut.$B$BEach of us vowed to look for Merithra, Arygos and Caelestrasz should the Scarab Wall ever fall.$B$BAnd fall it did... and so we came.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11063 SET `male_text`='Shouldn\'t you be saving the world?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11064 SET `male_text`='<Narain holds an unopened envelope to his forehead.>$B$BWhat is... Mmmm... Velvet!$B$BAm I right?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11065 SET `male_text`='Don\'t tell me! Shhh! You are here about the Ashbringer?!? Yes... Yes... No! My bad.$B$BWhat can I help you with, $r?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11066 SET `male_text`='Narain Soothfancy, at your service! Retired engineer and master soothsayer! I can tell your future before it even happens!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11067 SET `male_text`='You are not worth my time, $n!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11074 SET `male_text`='%s sets eyes on $n!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11075 SET `male_text`='Hehehe, how you doin\' mon. You gonna help Pele\'keiki great deal he be thinkin\'. We be needin\' a bombastic amount of the firebloom herb to be preparin\' right for the Ahn\'Qiraj War. The Horde, they say, \'Pele\'keiki, you get us $2051w of the fire petals right quick\'.$B$BPele\'keiki tell you now, he only have $2050w firebloom, but you gonna add to that real soon, right mon?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11076 SET `male_text`='Pele\'keiki know, it seem impossible even to him, but we be havin\' all that firebloom the Horde be wantin\' for the war. If you not be feelin\' too lazy, Pele\'keiki think you be helpin\' out the others here. They sure to have many things they be wantin\' you to get for them.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11077 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Ah, there you are. I was told to expect help, so please listen closely. The situation is this: I\'ve been tasked with gathering $2055w purple lotus in preparation for the coming war in Ahn\'Qiraj. To date we have $2054w.$B$BActually going into the field and collecting the flowers will be up to you and those like you. I am needed here to see that they are properly maintained and to find new, creative applications for their use against the silithid and whatever else awaits us there.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11078 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='We\'re filled to capacity on purple lotus, $c. Go ask one of the others if they need your help, and leave me to my studies. There is no time to waste!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11079 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='You\'re here to help with the heavy leather for the Ahn\'Qiraj war effort, are you, $c? Good, good. As you can see I\'ve collected $2066w, but we\'re going to need $2067w in total. That\'s a lot of skinning my friend, so I hope that your knife is sharp. The leather will go to all sorts of uses for making our war materiel and ensuring our success.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11080 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Ah, that\'s sweet of you mon, but we already got all the heavy leather that we need. And here I\'m sure that your knife is still sharp. Maybe you can put it to use helping the others with their collections, no?  Have a good one!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11081 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='An unspeakable horror dwells here, mortal.  C\'Thun and his worshippers are not just an affront to nature, their existence presages destruction for Azeroth as we know it.$B$BMerithra sacrificed herself a thousand years ago along with Caelestrasz and Arygos because they knew this as well.  We\'re here because of our oath to return for them, but we\'re also here because C\'Thun must be stopped!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11082 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Lok\'tar, $c, I have important information! There\'s a war coming at Ahn\'Qiraj and we need to get ready for it. I\'m here collecting all of the thick leather that I can get my hands on. Right now we have $2070w, but the Warchief has tasked me with the gathering of $2071w. As you can see, I\'m a little short.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11083 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='If you have more thick leather, I\'m sorry but you\'ve come too late. We have all that we need, but before you go would you check with the others here? There\'s likely someone that still needs your help with their own collecting.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11084 SET `male_text`='Hello, $c. I trust that you bring good tidings concerning the Ahn\'Qiraj War preparations. I myself have been placed in charge of all accumulation of rugged leather for the Horde; a task to which I feel uniquely qualified. Never underestimate the utility of a sharpened knife.$B$BAs to the rugged leather, we currently have $2073w out of $2074w needed.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11085 SET `male_text`='Such a pity, and here I\'ll wager that you sharpened your knife special in anticipation of slicing a few skins for me. Alas, we\'ve already gathered all of the rugged leather necessary, $c. Do make yourself useful though, and check with the others here to see if they have any other collection tasks to send you on.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11086 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='I find the ocean floor to be very peaceful.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11087 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='It\'s so lovely to see you again, $n! I really can\'t thank you enough for delivering that message to my dear little gnome.$B$BWould you like to hear a song? It will make traveling in the rough seas much easier!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11088 SET `male_text`='That would be wonderful! Thank you, Meridith.', `female_text`='That would be wonderful! Thank you, Meridith.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11089 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Lovely song, isn\'t it?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11090 SET `male_text`='Ah, $c, good to see you. We need assistance here with gathering supplies in preparation for the impending war at Ahn\'Qiraj. I\'ve been asked to put together a great many first aid field kits, and the primary component I need is wool bandages. I already have some, $2079w to be exact, but I need to collect $2080w.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11091 SET `male_text`='I thank you for your inquiry, but I already have all of the wool bandages necessary for the war effort. I suggest that you ask around though; there are many here that could probably still use your aid.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11092 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Hello, $c, good of you to show up. Allow me to be succinct; we are gathering supplies for the Ahn\'Qiraj war effort. We wouldn\'t want to have more casualties than necessary, now would we? I have the responsibility of coordinating the collection of $2086w mageweave bandages. To date we have garnered $2085w. Care to assist?';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11093 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='How unfortunate; it would appear that we have collected all of the mageweave bandages necessary. Perhaps you can go sell them on the auction house? But before you go, be a good $g boy : girl; and check with the other collectors present. They may have an errand to send you off on.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11094 SET `male_text`='I shall take my secrets to the grave with me!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11095 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='The Earth Mother provides, but at times, a $c needs a little extra help to survive. Thus, I am collecting all of the runecloth bandages that we can in preparation for the looming war at Ahn\'Qiraj. As of now we have gathered $2089w on our way to collecting a total of $2090w.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11096 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='It is very kind of you to ask after our needs, $c. It would appear though that we have collected all of the runecloth bandages we feel we\'ll need of the war. May I ask that you inquire around with some of the other collectors and lend them your aid if needed? Ancestors watch over you.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11097 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Grrr, what do you want, $r? Oh, you must be here about the lean wolf steaks for the impending Ahn\'Qiraj War. Yes, you heard right, I\'m collecting them, what about it? Do you have a fresh stack for me? I only need $2096w, and it looks like we have $2095w right now.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11098 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Looks like we have as many lean wolf steaks as the Horde wants. They told me to pack up what we have here and ready it to be shipped it out to Cenarion Hold in Silithus. But it looks like some of the others here might still be collecting whatever it is that they\'re in charge of. Go bug one of them.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11099 SET `male_text`='Ja mon, I be collectin\' up the fishy-fishy for the Horde. They gettin\' ready for big war in the desert at Ahn\'Qiraj, and askin\' me to get them $2103w of the spotted yellowtail. But right now we only be havin\' $2102w. You here to help?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11100 SET `male_text`='Heya, $c! Lookin\' like we got all the spotted yellowtail that we be needin\' for that war. Maybe you going to some of the other collectors \'round here and askin\' them if they be needin\' your help?', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11101 SET `male_text`='Greetings, $c. It is good to see you interested in helping with the war effort. The collectors here are organizing the gathering of various stockpiles of goods so that we will be prepared when the time comes.$B$BI am in charge of obtaining $2106w baked salmon to store away for those involved in the fighting at Ahn\'Qiraj. The last time that I counted, we had collected $2105w.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11102 SET `male_text`='It is good of you to ask, $c, but we already have all of the baked salmon that we\'ll need for the war. Perhaps you would be kind enough to check with the other collectors here; they are sure to have something that they could use your help with.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11103 SET `male_text`='I do not have time to waste, $c; there is a war at Ahn\'Qiraj to prepare for. If you are going to help, we are collecting singed corestones from the Molten Core. I need to gather a total of $2110w, and currently have $2109w.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11104 SET `male_text`='The guilds of the Horde have pulled together and accomplished this task already $c. We have all of the singed corestones necessary for our war materiel. Make yourself useful by asking the other collectors here if they need your aid.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11105 SET `male_text`='Now is the time when the year is new and the moon shines bright.$B$BIt is our time... when the ancients awake.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11106 SET `male_text`='No hello for your old friend, Narain? Who were you expecting???', `female_text`='';
