UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11880 SET `male_text`='So you\'re looking to relearn what you forgot, eh? Or maybe learn what you were never taught? I know just the thing, $n. Over by Steamwheedle port, to the east, you\'ll find a magical book in Narain\'s hut called \"Soothsaying for Dummies.\" Give it a read.$B$B<Nixx winks.>$B$BYou\'ll find all that you need to know and then some...', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11881 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='You\'re never going to stop coming after me, are you?  Fine, but you won\'t take me down without a fight!';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11882 SET `male_text`='Teach you the ways of gnomish engineering? Not going to happen! Not this gnome, anyway. You have a stink on you, $n. Maybe this is the pity talking but I will offer some advice.$B$BIn the Tanaris desert you\'ll find a hut that belongs to Narain Soothfancy. In that hut is a magical book that has been known to do wonderous things. Find that book and you may yet learn the gnomish way.', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11883 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='I didn\'t mean to drag you into this, $n.  Ever since we took on a job to steal Lord Valthalak\'s spellbook, everyone involved has wound up dead or missing.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11884 SET `male_text`='Teach you gnomish engineering? I don\'t have time for this nonsense. You only get one chance with Oglethorpe and you blew that, didn\'t you?$B$BYou\'ll have to head to Tanaris and find Narain Soothfancy\'s hut. In that hut is a magical book that might be able to jostle whatever is left of your brain and reconnect you with what you\'ve lost.$B$BNow get lost!', `female_text`='';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11885 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Trying to find out more about my predicament has been nearly impossible.  The smuggler that hired us has vanished and Anthion Harmon, our mercenary company\'s leader, is dead.';
UPDATE `broadcast_text` WHERE `entry`=11888 SET `male_text`='', `female_text`='Come to think about it, most everyone involved is dead.  I\'ll understand if you don\'t want to be involved in any of this, $n.';
